(11, 'top-5-stocks-to-invest-in-this-march', 'Mon, 08 Mar 2021 14:56:53 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Last few months have been a series of ups and downs for the financial markets. Whether its forex, stocks or commodities, the trends have been quite inconsistent overall. Who thought Bitcoin would set a new record price one day and then 3 days later decline by a massive $11000 amount leading towards a billion dollar loss for investors in one single day!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Same has been the case for US dollar that is fighting to maintain a competitive position in the market but is failing due to many reasons: The biggest of all, Covid19. Even though Joe Bidden successfully introduced the $1.9 trillion stimulus in Parliament this Saturday, US is facing major threats that are keeping a dollar in a tight grip. As a result, the US based companies are facing existential threats which must be taken care of quickly.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In today’s post we will talk about the best investment opportunities for the month of March. We have carefully collected data from various sources and critically analyzed each stock to recommend you the best profitable trades for this month. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/gilly-wcWN29NufMQ-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><strong>NVDA – NVidia Corporation&nbsp;</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first on our list is Nvidia Corporation. The brand has gained popularity since the last few years and is expected to grow stronger in future. Even though NVDA has faced a strong bearish trend recently which has pulled it down 2.35% in 2021, it is expected to make a comeback in the following months due to its GPU drivers and higher revenue expectations.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If we analyze the historical data of NVDA, its revenue has grown from $11716M in 2018 to $1665M in 2020. This is further expected to grow in 2021 with a forecasted value of $2000M which shows how important it is for investors looking for long-term gains. Furthermore, its operating income and earnings per share has also increased in the same proportion within the last 3 years. A strong bullish trend might be noticed soon so it is recommended to buy NVDA this month.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":2} -->\n<ol start=\"2\"><li><strong>General Motors (GM)</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Just like NVDA, GM also faced a bearish trend recently and closed 2.66% lower this week but unlike NVDA, GM has been experiencing a strong bullish trend since the beginning of 2021 and it is important to note that GM has gained approximately 30% in value till now. A major reason behind this bullish wave is the announcement by the automobile giants that revealed the company’s plan of electric vehicles.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Previously, GM has been manufacturing famous car brands such as Buick, Cadillac, GMC etc. After analyzing its financial statements we found a very interesting development. GM’s overall revenue has decreased from around $147000M to around $122400M during the last 3 years but its operating income has increased from $6293M to $8559M in the same financial period.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":3} -->\n<ol start=\"3\"><li><strong>Alibaba (BABA) Stocks</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>February has not been the month for Alibaba and just like the stocks mentioned above, BABA also faced a strong bearish trend in February, giving an opportunity to the investors to buy for a long-term gain. Having said that, Alibaba stocks are still the strongest stocks with a huge potential in the future in terms of profit maximization.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The company stocks are expected to increase in value by 30%-37% in the next 2 years which makes it the right choice for long-term investors. It’s revenue potentials have been growing consistently over the past few years and it is expected to become bullish this March.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":4} -->\n<ol start=\"4\"><li><strong>Goldman Sachs (GS)</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As economy regains its strength after the disastrous effects of Coronavirus are now weakening overtime, banks are expected to play a vital role. With every new day comes a positive vaccine breakthrough in different parts of the world and when we talk about Goldman Sachs, JNJ and NVAX breakthroughs have given it an opportunity to restore its interest margins yet again.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This development has made the GS stocks very important in terms of a long-term investment approach. The bank is expected to rise again soon and the stocks are expected to ride a bull sooner than one can expect. This makes it an important stock to buy this March!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":5} -->\n<ol start=\"5\"><li><strong>Netflix (NFLX)</strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Who doesn’t know about Netflix? Especially, when you’re stuck in quarantine and have nothing else to do but to watch new seasons and movies all day, all night. In a recent development, Netflix has made a surprising comeback after it lost 1 billion watch hours in the past. With a massive subscriber growth and better than expected net earnings, Netflix is back in the game and ready to strike!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NFLX revenue has grown during the past 3 years and even though its 0.41% lower in 2021 compared to the previous year, the stock is expected to gain strength very soon. Right now is the right time to buy it so what are you waiting for? Go ahead and do it now!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These were the 5 best stocks to invest in this March. If you found this article helpful, share it with your friends and family and keep visiting for more interesting content!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Top 5 stocks to invest in this March', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Stockwatch', '1623072024_gilly-wcWN29NufMQ-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:20:24'),
(12, '2021-the-best-era-for-investment-in-artificial-intelligence-market', 'Tue, 16 Mar 2021 08:29:53 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The world faced a huge setback in terms of economy and overall financial disruption was observed in the year 2020 because of the outbreak of Coronavirus. In the final months of the past year, however, the market seemed to have been getting back on track because of major reforms in terms of technology and global digital investments. Hence, the year 2021 is also expected to be one of the most important years in the history of times because the common public has turned to Digi-centric ways to maintain the social distancing, allowing more focus towards automation and digital marketing.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Artificial intelligence, which was once brushed off under the rug and considered a futuristic technology, is seen evolving in the present times, used extensively by data scientists. The human data, i.e. customers’ behavior to a certain stimulus like search patterns, hashtags frequently used, etc. are put into use in order to form enhanced automated virtual assistants. This automation allows less human involvement and more workload on the machines, given the fact that the algorithm keeps getting updated to cope with the gigantic amount of Metadata generated every single day. The data analysis and digital transformation also enable an understanding of how humans function; the way they think, interact with other people, their interests, how they feel and respond in a given situation.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This digital transformation has enabled a better customer operational experience since it is focused more on human needs and how they function, e.g.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Machine learning and Artificial Intelligence have put to use together <strong>for Autonomous driverless cars</strong> like Google’s Waymo, Proton X70, DFSK Glory 580 Pro, Hyundai Tuscon, Tesla cars, etc. McKinsey predicts that by the year 2030, there will be a wide majority of 15% cars driven autonomously.</li><li><strong>Uber and Microsoft are using&nbsp;Knightscope K5 robots</strong>&nbsp;for security purposes. They are assigned to “patrol parking lots and large outdoor areas to predict and prevent crime. The robots can read license plates, report suspicious activity, and collect data to report to their owners.”</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Are these R2-D2-like bots accessible to the common man? To your surprise, it is super affordable and charges much less than a human guard, for just&nbsp;$7 an hour</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Use of AI for <strong>Cloud Computing Technologies</strong></li><li>The Tech Giants- Amazon, Facebook, and Google are investing all the time more in <strong>AI-enabled chips</strong> that would be able to support efficient query processing for rapid analytics</li><li><strong>Autonomous Payment Methods</strong> (that is very crucial in today’s pandemic times)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>AI works through predictive data analysis that countenances in the steps towards perfection through upgrades in the internal and operational functionality to achieve an improved customer experience. A poll was conducted recently that shows that out of the 68% individuals who were well in check with digital transformations, 95% of people said that \"digital transformation funds are best spent on improving the buyer experience\", while a high 98% endorsed it as the preeminent method to uplift sales.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><img width=\"624\" height=\"444\" alt=\"Reasons for adopting AI\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/maAGztv4r_n-lCuFSym1dZRXumcBcLwCnlgqV0TEnH8Mblf3BuINtiQPfzRTwKpcxWf6lNZ88bISokmW9fIfd0r3po1Y2g-Wzejj14e8EgZn0gBflvTPG96fugLnoKYbHnkKLVo\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Artificial Intelligence is, without any doubt, the heart of global industry today. It is only going to flourish in the future, and will probably take over the world, causing many to lose their jobs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '2021- The Best Era for Investment in Artificial Intelligence Market', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Investment,Stockwatch', '1623071996_gabriel-benois-qnWPjzewewA-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:19:56'),
(13, 'social-media-platforms-their-economic-contribution', 'Tue, 16 Mar 2021 08:35:51 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If someone had said that hiring and recruitment for brands would be done in days instead of the traditional lengthy process that requires considerations of months 15 years ago, we would have definitely laughed it off. However, in today’s era, it is not only do-able but also the priority of the majority of businesses. Social media platforms gave rise to the prospect for online hiring, making it possible for businesses to shorten their employment processes and the creation of new job openings. Who could fathom the existence of a designation of a “Social Media Manager” a decade ago?&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to the Office of National Statistics (ONS), the social media usage by the customers makes 66% of the total, just in the United Kingdom. This popularity is also backed by research carried out by the global WebIndex stating that “Social media users are now spending an average of 2 hours and 24 minutes everyday multi-networking across an average of 8 social networks and messaging apps<strong><em>.”</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":179,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dole777-EQSPI11rf68-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-179\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Increased ad-spending across social media platforms</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yuval Ben-Itzhak- the President at Socialbakers said that \"Brands dramatically increased their investment in social media advertising in Q4. At its Q4 peak, worldwide ad-spend increased by 50.3% compared to the holiday peak in Q4 2019,\"&nbsp;One thing is for sure, that companies are not spending that huge chunk of money on social media platforms just for the fun, as they clearly have considerable financial gains that push them in this direction. According to a researcher, Facebook and Google control almost 60% of e-commerce, which surpasses the traditional leaders in market valuation. With so much audience investing their time and money on social media platforms, not investing now in this domain will surely be an unwise thing to do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Eliminating barriers to entry</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social Media helps in the establishment of new businesses by pushing down various barriers that once caused major hindrance in the overall process, for example, you do not need to buy or rent out a physical store anymore. Heck, offices are also virtually operated! You also do not need to pay to get out the information regarding your business instead all the latest and trending news is publicized on social media platforms. The latest trend has shown that Instagram has rapidly become the hub for business investors as it enables people and companies to broadcast their own media brands, aiding in a competent progressive environment according to the customer demands, quicker than they would have ever thought as they get to interact with people directly and get reviewed, which enables constant evolution of quality standards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Cashing in on the associations</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whenever companies want someone to be the face of their brand, they choose someone with enough fame and credibility in their relevant audiences that could help them establish their name and form concrete grounds in the hearts of their target customers, which can elevate their brand’s reputation hence uplifting monetary values. Research has found out that a consumer goes through a lot of stages and evaluates his options carefully while buying; one of it being the fact that he considers, rather unknowingly, his perception or association with a certain brand, making it favorable for that brand as they’ve got your trust.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The platforms that emerged as investment sites in the eyes of investors last year include Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, and the most recent ones; Tiktok and Snapchat! As researched by<em> Digital 2020 July Global snapshot “</em>4.57 billion people around the world&nbsp;now use the internet, and of those users,&nbsp;346 million new users have come online&nbsp;within the last 12 months”. That is a whole lot of users that companies should not overlook as they can help make content go viral; supported by some “shares” and “hashtags”, news travels faster than it ever has. This has it made essential for the brands and companies to seek audience approval to be politically correct and to avoid cultural misappropriation, so tread carefully but tread you must!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Social Media Platforms & their Economic Contribution', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Economics,Social Media', '1623071968_gabriel-benois-qnWPjzewewA-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:19:28'),
(14, 'nasdaq-is-back-in-action-a-huge-jump-expected', 'Tue, 16 Mar 2021 08:56:06 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nasdaq has shown signs of a bullish trend last week and it is expected to continue its journey next week. However, the bullish journey might be welcomed by a bear trap later on and today in this article we will explain exactly how that could happen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On March 13, 2021 Nasdaq experienced a strong bullish grip just as the trading session was about to end. The last half hour proved to be a game changer for it. Consistent buying allowed the moving averages to edge towards the new highs of the day and Nasdaq was soon under influence of the bulls!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":191,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/tech-daily-wcHwSy_JE4c-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-191\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What happened on 13th March? An in-depth analysis</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While tech was deep under water for most of the day, SP500 helped to net out its negative effects. On one hand, Nasdaq COMP lagged by -0.6% and on the other hand, SP500 moved up by 0.1% ending in a bullish cycle.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The huge cyclical price moves allowed DOW DJI to push the moving averages higher by 0.9% whereas Boeing and Goldman alone moved up by 150 points.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>March 13 was optimistic for all 3 indexes as they moved higher than the opening positions and ended above the initial expected levels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The 10 year treasury yield saw a 10 basis point appreciation and as a result, equities increased at the later part of the day, keeping the yields near the highest levels of the day. This movement came as a surprise to the investors who had not expected Nasdaq to show signs of optimism. As a result, many of the investors opened long positions to gain profits in the coming week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>\"US 10-year note yields leaving behind all other breakouts from six-month ranges except the 1994 experience,\"</em>&nbsp;said Ben Breitholtz, a data scientist at Arbor Data science.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite being on a bumpy road that day, Nasdaq managed to secure a 3.1% gain. Even though this seems like positive news for the bulls, certain developments have raised excitement in the bears who are now ringing an alarm for the bulls.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Will the tables turn?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now Nasdaq seems to be in a strong bullish position but as we move towards next week, many analysts are predicting a 20% fall for Nasdaq if the bond yield reaches the 2% level. According to the past trends, as Bond yield increased, Nasdaq 100 depreciated. This natural mechanism is raising many questions in the minds of the investors and a bear trap can be expected soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the 10 year treasury bond yield reaches 2% it would increase the BAA bond yields to 4.5% as a result. To overcome this inconsistency, Nasdaq would have to fall by 20%. Having said that, this mechanism might turn out to be a reality soon but it won\'t appear easily. A 2% 10 year treasury bond is quite difficult to achieve as of now and so, Nasdaq might continue to walk on the bullish path without facing any obstacles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We suggest you follow the bullish trends for now but keep looking at the bond yields to save yourself from huge losses in the future. For more updates, keep visiting our website and don\'t forget to share it with your friends and family!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nasdaq is back in action - a huge jump expected', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Investment,Stockwatch', '1623071955_tech-daily-wcHwSy_JE4c-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:19:15'),
(15, 'will-2021-be-optimistic-for-the-investors-how-high-the-stock-market-will-go', 'Tue, 16 Mar 2021 09:05:32 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As we all know, the stock market in 2020 was defined by Code-19. The virus is still lingering in 2021 which is going to have a volatile impact on the stock market. Many investors thought it would go away by the first quarter but it is not going away anywhere. However, the good news for the investors is that we are expecting some normalcy in the return as the vaccine is already there and this will directly impact the gains. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bram-naus-oqnVnI5ixHg-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Will Stocks Market show bullish or bearish trends?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wall street journal is also hopeful about a bumpy but high settling trend. According to the survey of CNBC, the average gain at the end of FY 2021 will be around 9.5%. As the current points level is 3,700 in S&amp;P it may increase as high as 4,300. However, the bank of America is of the view that S&amp;P could go as far as 3,800 points.. This is definitely a good sign and it will help in boosting the economic growth. The individuals are feeling liberated after successful vaccination trials and various countries around the world have lifted the pandemic related restrictions. People are feeling freedom and no longer afraid of travelling, shopping and are coming back to normal life.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is also a fact that this road to normalcy is bumpy and jumpy. 2021’s start is favorable for the stocks markets. After assurance of the Federal Reserves that it will not change the interest rates has set a positive pace in the market.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now that things seemed smooth until now, it is still risky for the investors. Because, the stock market is like an animal which is forward looking and any volatility will shake the investors.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Expected Market Return in 2021:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As we all know, investors are still feeling aftershocks of the wild-ride in the stock market. The returns dropped by 36% in the first quarter and recovered by 59% and generated nearly a market return of 17.5% in total.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This double digit is a lining in the grey sky because it shows the positive expectations and confidence of investors amid pandemic.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also, this pandemic hit the US hard as many people died, became unemployed, businesses were lost and many small units were shut down. The bullish trend is set to grow and stay in 2021 because it is expected that 50% of the US population is going to be vaccinated by April and this is going to be a game changer. The experts are of the view that best days follow the worst days in the stock market. The technology sector has witnessed a momentum during the pandemic as dominated the market by bullish trends. The stock decelerated after the vaccination production. This is just an example of the market volatility of stocks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, we expect a recovering trend in S&amp;P and as the monetary policy is favorable and from the market\'s perspective a smooth business without hiccups is&nbsp; what we look forward to.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Will 2021 be optimistic for the Investors how high the stock market will go?', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Investment,Strategic Financial Management', '1623071940_bram-naus-oqnVnI5ixHg-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:19:00'),
(16, 'tesla-stocks-should-it-be-a-buy', 'Tue, 16 Mar 2021 09:08:23 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tesla is an American clean energy company which also produces electric vehicles.&nbsp; The products of the company include electric cars, energy batteries for home and industrial use, solar panels and tiles and various other related products. Tesla joined the S&amp; P 500 as the fifth largest prestigious member on Monday 21st Dec 2021. When the electric car maker joined the benchmark S&amp;P Index and began trading, its stock fell by 5% despite being the largest new entry.&nbsp; Its stock was trading at $ 695 and closed on the same value. However, it fell to $ 665 which is almost 5% in pre-market trading.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This disappointed the investors as they were expecting a decent rise in the stock. After the sharp dip in the stock the market became volatile and they were hesitant to buy the shares as the speculated bearish trend will be consistent for some time. However, Tesla beat the expectation and started showing a rise and turned bullish gradually in the first quarter of 2021.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tesla has a Transformative but volatile Year:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The entry of Tesla in the benchmark index of S&amp; P 500 was a big news for the industry and investors. The electric car maker was named as the wild fish y the analysts as they expected overall volatility in the stocks because of Tesla. As they anticipated it will put downward pressure on the index on other stocks. The addition of Tesla in S&amp;P is a historic event as it is a $ 20 billion company that has witnessed remarkable growth in 6 consecutive quarters. Its share soared to 750% growth in one year. When the company started trading its 200 million shares were picked up and sold in a single session which is a record time.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The analysts are hopeful that Tesla will have a bullish year as it has created a gain of 15%. They are of the view that Tesla will go high as $ 1,200 in next 12 months. This is just the prediction based on the historic performance and future expectations but the analysts that are of bearish view say that Tesla stock is actually overrated and investors must invest in some other stocks like healthcare.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They believe that Tesla stocks prices soar more because of enthusiasm of buyers than its ability to generate and deliver profits. Despite all the criticism on its actual value and performance in the stocks market, Tesla has the ability to move 1 point in the index with $ 11.11 move.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Bearish Trend is prevailing:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tesla has faced a volatile quarter despite all the hope and its stocks are facing bearish trends since January 27. The share which rose to $ 883 till Jan 26 has now reached below $ 700. It is the same level when the company entered the benchmark index and wiped out all previous profits. However, the stock is selling off for various reasons such as Elon Musk’s $1.5 billion investment in bitcoin, Model Y pricing and increased competition.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tesla is a game changer and never ceases to surprise investors. So we hope it will change into a bull soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Tesla Stocks, should it be a buy?', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Investment,Stockwatch', '1623071980_bram-van-oost-4xM5cytsdMo-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:19:40'),
(17, 'dow-jumps-150-points-building-on-gains-from-the-last-week', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 15:37:07 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dow, short for the Dow Jones Industrial Average (DIJA), is an index of the stock market that involves itself in tracking 30 companies trading on the New York Stock Exchange and the NASDAQ. These companies are publicly owned blue-chip companies that are a major source of financial news and give the direction of the stock market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Monday, shortly after the market opened, shares of some giant tech companies rose on Wall Street resulting in DIJA gaining 153 points and closing at 26,024.96; the rise was calculated to be 0.6%. Nasdaq closed at 10,056.47 equivalent to 1.1% and S&amp;P closed its session at 0.7% increase at 3117.86.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple’s shares went up 2% which is recorded to be the highest. This might be due to the company’s insight on adopting more polished strategies for its Mac, as it will no longer be using Intel chips. The latest version of iOS has also been revealed recently. Microsoft gained more than 2% and remained on top at Dow. Netflix reported being risen by 2.6%, while Amazon went up by 1.5%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":214,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/patrick-hendry-6xeDIZgoPaw-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-214\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Industries brutally affected by the pandemic are reaching a new high!</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Southwest Airlines is up 2% and JetBlue is up 4%. Some big retail giants also saw the brighter side of the picture such as GAP which went up by 8.3% and Walmart by 1% following an upgrade by UBS. Results for Global stocks varies throughout, e.g. SSE Composite at Shanghai fell short by 1% while FTSE &amp; CAC 40 of UK and France, respectively, crept up by 0.1%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some stocks such as Mosaic – a big name amongst fertilizer companies, went up 5%. CBRE – a real estate investment firm went up 3%. However, Eli Lilly – the largest manufacturer of psychiatric medications, could not provide attractive results for a new Alzheimer’s drug that they were experimenting with and hence underperformed by 7%.<br /></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bitcoin’s prices fell 6% this Monday morning when almost everything else claimed victory. This contrasts highly with the past week’s performance of bitcoin which was reported to have increased by more than 10% and achieving $61,000 on Sunday. This can also be credited to India’s expected ban on cryptocurrency trading and mining.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Is Market being used as a proxy?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kim Forest – founder of Bokeh Capital remarked: “Investors are using the market as a proxy for getting back to normal. If too many people get sick, they’re going to shut down parts of the economy and the market will react.” He is pointing towards an extremely valid point as the number of coronavirus cases is increasing again. Some countries are even experiencing their 3<sup>rd</sup> wave and this upsurge of new cases raises questions regarding this sudden global economic recovery. According to the data collected by John Hopkins University, United States has come across more than 30,000 reported coronavirus cases which is the highest number since May 1<sup>st</sup>, 2020. This upsurge of cases in some states caused Apple to shut-down its stores while other businesses slowed down as well. However, this rise of 150 points does hint towards the financial recovery of the market. The best we can do is keep our fingers crossed for now and hope for the best!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Dow jumps 150 points – Building on gains from the last week!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Stockwatch', '1623071890_patrick-hendry-6xeDIZgoPaw-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:18:10'),
(18, 'lg-s-rationale-for-investing-4-5-million-in-another-ev-battery-plant', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 15:41:18 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LG has decided to invest around $4.5 billion in its own business in the United States of America, which will result in the increase of its production capacity of batteries by the end of 2025. This expansion will also yield around 10,000 new job opportunities. Sub-contractors are also reported to get an additional 70GWh which would be fruitful results for all the parties involved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LG Energy Solution plans on furthering its cell production capacity by entering a Joint Venture with General Motors. The site decided for the manufacturing of next-generation EV cells by incorporating advanced technology in the US, where pouch cell batteries will be used in EVs and ESS – Energy Storage Systems, whereas cylindrical cell EV batteries will also be produced as they are high in demand these days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":217,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/riccardo-annandale-7e2pe9wjL9M-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-217\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Competitive advantage - </strong>LG’s first research facility required an investment of $600 Million that enabled the production capacity of 5GWh at its very first plant in Michigan, built in the year 2012. Later in 2019, the company joined hands with GM to construct another battery plant located in Ohio which required an investment of around $2.3 billion, which is hoped to be completed by 2022 creating an annual capacity of 35GWh. However, the latest venture i.e. their second joint venture; The Green Field Project will incorporate a production capacity of over 110GWh thus allowing them to stay in the game and be able to compete with their rival companies in the rapidly increasing EV battery market. Robinson- Senior Director at LG Electronics remarks; “This expansion speaks to the rapid increase in electric vehicle sales, and the supply chain concerns automakers have. This additional capacity ensures GM will have the cells it needs to deliver on its electric vehicle ambitions.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LG Energy Solution says that the plans are currently under discussion; the basic driver for this expansion was the announcement of the automakers around the world which hinted at the manufacturing of new EV models. Sam Abuelsamid, Research Analyst at Michigan remarked; “In order to build all those EVs, they’re all going to need batteries”. LG has been selling batteries to many companies around the world. All these companies are big names like Audi, Ford, GM, Volkswagen and Porsche, etc. who feel the need to constantly experiment with their EV models. This increasing competition drives the companies to keep enhancing their products. According to Abuelsamid’s forecast of increasing EVs per year, 2035 will bring with itself a high demand for batteries. This would put increasing pressure on the companies to meet the demand as the current rate at which EVS are produced is 1.2 million per year, on average.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Like other industries, the EV industry was also affected by the Covid-19 which caused its sales to drop significantly. According to GM, it plans on selling out 1 million electric vehicles per year in the United States of America and China. This sudden release of EVs in the market, conjoined with the improving conditions of government policies, will increase the sales of EVs this year, hence mitigating the effects caused by the pandemic to this industry!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'LG’s rationale for investing $4.5 Million in another EV Battery plant', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Don\'t Miss,Investment', '1623071871_riccardo-annandale-7e2pe9wjL9M-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:17:51'),
(19, 'who-will-benefit-from-biden-s-1-9-trillion-rescue-package', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 15:44:58 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A relief package was promoted last week by President Biden, Vice President Harris, and their spouses during their travel trip labeled as “<strong>Help is Here” </strong>throughout various states within the United States of America; including Las Vegas, Burlington, N.J., Philadelphia, Atlanta, and Denver. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":220,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/markus-spiske-g6ccZL5QNZg-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-220\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>American Rescue Plan is being promoted by the White House as the democratic leaders- President Biden and Vice President Harris work towards making the roll-out of the $1.9 trillion Bill successful. This marks as the first major strategic accomplishment of Biden’s term of presidency which is backed by law and subject to implementation all across the United States of America.&nbsp; In one of the recent instances, President Biden remarked \"It\'s critical to demonstrate that government can function and deliver prosperity, security, and opportunity for the people of this country.\"&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Legislation in question will be responsible for providing relief to those being affected throughout the country through direct payments to make the process hassle-free for the residents, along with the incorporation of extended unemployment benefits in reference to the damage caused by the pandemic causing joblessness, along with the availability of Coronavirus vaccination all across the country. The coronavirus recovery package includes $1400 checks to millions of eligible recipients in addition to the $600 payments that were sent out earlier this month, making it a total of $2000. This bill will also include expanded child tax credit, in support of schools and businesses, working-class would immensely benefit from this bill as Biden states; \"For the first time in a long time, this bill puts working people in this nation first\".&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Highlights of the Recovery Act:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>$15 billion will be provided to create a new grant program for&nbsp;small business owners.</li><li>$15 billion would be set aside to help the families in paying their rents, utilities, and increased costs due to the pandemic for their PPEs.</li><li>$20 billion be given to the hardest-hit public transit agencies</li><li>A 15% increase in food stamps would be extended till September 2021.</li><li>Affordable Care Act\'s premium subsidies will be expanded so that enrollees don\'t have to pay more than 8.5% of their income for coverage. This would help those who lost their health insurance as a result of losing their jobs.</li><li>Around $20 billion will be invested in a&nbsp;national vaccination program, including launching community vaccination centers around the country and mobile units in hard-to-reach areas. Funds for hiring 100,000 public health workers would also be provided</li><li>Biden will provide $350 billion to state, local, and territorial governments to keep their frontline workers employed, distribute the vaccine, increase testing, reopen schools and maintain vital services</li><li>For childcare, 425 billion emergency funds would be provided.&nbsp;</li><li>Low- and moderate-income families will be provided $25 billion in rental assistance. Another $5 billion would be set aside to help those struggling to pay rent to help them out in paying their utility bills</li><li>Minimum wage is also proposed to be increased to $15 per hour</li><li>Paid sick and family leave benefits would be reinstated</li><li>Unemployed individuals will receive $400 per week.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gene Sperling, the man of the hour:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While Biden has gained major popularity in America as according to Marist survey, 62% of Americans approve of Biden and his handling techniques of the pandemic, for the rollout of this recovery act, Economist Gene Sperling, who is also the Democratic adviser, is chosen by the President to oversee the smooth delivery of the said promises. Stating the responsibilities of his advisor, Biden said that \"Gene will be on the phone with mayors and governors, red states, blue states — a source of constant communication, a source of guidance and support, and above all a source of accountability for all of us to get the job done.\" Biden also noted that Sperling was also responsible for certain bills in President Obama’s time and worked honestly without waste or fraud, therefore,&nbsp; he approves of him and commemorates his compliments by calling him a “gifted manager” who is “ready to get to work”. Biden views this law as, “only the beginning [of his efforts].\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Who will benefit from Biden’s $1.9 trillion Rescue Package?', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Economics,Uncategorized', '1623071857_markus-spiske-g6ccZL5QNZg-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:17:37'),
(20, 'philly-fed-manufacturing-index-to-achieve-new-highs-in-50-years', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 15:52:39 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In February, the Philadelphia Federal Reserve’s business activity was reported to be at 23.1. However, in March, it has taken a sudden turn and has jumped to 51.8. Reports show that this is the highest reading since 1973! Surveys like the National Institute for Supply Management manufacturing index are composites that are based on components; however, the Philly Fed Index is based upon business conditions. This month the subcomponents of the Philly Fed index have been recorded to have gained quite strappingly. Economists were not too optimistic and had forecasted that it would remain flat for this month as well, as stated by Philly Fed: “Nearly 59% of the firms reported increases in current activity this month (up from 35% last month), while only 7% reported decreases (down from 11%).”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":223,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/science-in-hd-HJI1fL4VCnI-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-223\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Some of the Major Happenings this March were:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Rise of barometer on new orders was reported to be 50.9 for March as opposed to 23.4 in February. This is the greatest number of orders in the last 50 years.</li><li>Improvement of the employment index for March as well as of two months before it. As stated by Philly Fed: “Nearly 32 percent of the responding firms reported increases in employment, while only 1 percent of the firms reported decreases. The current workweek index increased 9 points to 39.7,”&nbsp;</li><li>The measure gauging the six-month outlook soared to 61.6 from 39.5 in the prior month.</li><li>The shipments index moved to 30.2 from 21.5 this February.</li><li>The Prices paid index rose to 75.9 for March. A stark difference from that of February, which was 54.4. According to analysts, this is the new high achieved since 1980. The prices-received index also moved up, although only by a less dramatic 15 points to 31.8.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The above statistics are gathered from the Philadelphia Fed’s home territory that includes around 13.3 million people and is spread across Delaware, Southern New Jersey, and Eastern and Central&nbsp;Pennsylvania<em>.&nbsp;</em><em><br /></em><em><br /></em><strong>Manufacturing getting back on the track</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>New York and Philadelphia regional indexes are used by Economists to measure the strength of the national ISM manufacturing index. This was reported to have achieved new highs and resulted in the fastest expansion since the world got hit by Coronavirus in 2019. According to the chief US economist at High-Frequency Economics Rubeela Farooqui <strong>“</strong>Overall, manufacturing is moving closer to pre-pandemic levels, driven by strong demand for goods, although ongoing supply chain bottlenecks remain a headwind.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>DIJA (-0.46%) and COMP (-3.02%) were mixed as yields on the 10-year Treasury note TMUBMUSD10Y (1.694%) kept pushing higher after Fed Chairman Jerome Powell’s press conference on Wednesday. Nasdaq, however, was down 1.38% in midday trading.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some say that this is all due to the economic policies of President Donald Trump who might have left the economy on a stronger footing than that was assumed otherwise. He put manufacturing at the top of his priorities and strengthened it due to which it is snowballing, even during the pandemic which has caused the business to come to a halt!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Philly Fed Manufacturing Index to achieve new Highs in 50 Years', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Uncategorized', '1623071837_science-in-hd-HJI1fL4VCnI-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:17:17');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `post_url`, `pubDate`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `post_author`, `post_category`, `post_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(21, 'boost-for-apple-the-french-privacy-fight', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 17:09:31 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was witnessed that Apple Nasdaq was boosted on this Wednesday. This happened because watch dog of France\'s antitrust turned down the request of the advertiser\'s to hang the latest privacy feature introduced by iPhone makers. However, it still faces some study into the question whether it is biased about it\'s own services and products.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The new feature in Apple iPhone\'s is named as \'App Tracking Transparency\'. This feature basically offers the users an experience of privacy. The users have the choice to block the advertisers. Advertisers usually have the access to track the users through various applications and this is what can be stopped by this latest feature.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":236,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/michal-kubalczyk-tdMu8W9NTnY-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-236\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As per the opinion of the giant tech of the US this feature has been facing discouragement from app developers, Facebook and start ups. Although, the feature is pro privacy and supports this major concern of the users but it has effected the above entities because these businesses depend a lot on advertising through tracking.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>IAB France, UDECAM, SRI and MMAF are some French groups which raised their concerned last year with the watchdog. According to these French&nbsp; groups this privacy feature would not be impacting the ability of Apple to get the targeted ads through the users of its very own iOS software, that too, without asking for their consent in advance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Watchdog Head and what she had to say:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Isabelle de Silva, the watchdog head had to say that she had worked professionally with CNIL data privacy regulators of France in order to decide upon the issue of turning down the request to hold the privacy feature.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Furthermore, it is said by her that CNIL analysed and estimated the pop up box which is placed by Apple that it has the ability to be advantageous to the users in an even bigger and complicated online environment of advertising. And it was brought forward in a very fair and unbiased manner exactly how the European Union has requested. By that we mean the GDPR Data protection rules.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She also stated that the date protection rules effected the decision of the watchdog to a huge extent. The fact that the authority acted against the investigator\'s recommendations of suspension of the privacy features of Apple, led to this situation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"There may be privacy washing, we\'re not naive,\" Isabella de Silva said. \"However, the GDPR is binding on us and as a member of a European legal system, I believe that everyone must take it into account.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Conclusion&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A decision is expected next year as the watchdog stated that it will still go on with the investigation on whether Apple is biased and unfairly favouring its own services and products.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, there were no immediate comments or statements made by Apple on what Isabella had said but it did anticipate and welcomed the stance and decision of watchdog in a statement that the privacy feature was surely in favour of the French users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The study was welcomed by the complainants even though they were not happy with the decision. Moreover, they stated negatively about the behaviour of Apple as it depicts an abuse or exploitation of it\'s super place. Consequently, developers being in the less dominant position have to agree to the terms set by Apple to watch their applications show the app store to be readily available for Apple Iphone customers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Boost for Apple - the French privacy fight', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Economics', '1623071816_michal-kubalczyk-tdMu8W9NTnY-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:16:56'),
(22, 'intel-announced-to-invest-20-billion-in-two-new-chip-factories', 'Mon, 29 Mar 2021 11:36:35 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the most pressing concerns of today, occurring worldwide, is the Chip shortage. To address this issue, Intel has established its dominance in the market by investing $20 billion in major manufacturing of semiconductors. Pat Gelsinger, the new CEO of Intel announced plans to outsource Intel’s chip production to third-party foundries and establishment of two new state-of-the-art chip factories (called fabs) in the Ocotillo facility in Arizona, plus a new branch of the company called Intel Foundry Services that will produce chips for other companies.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":242,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/slejven-djurakovic-0uXzoEzYZ4I-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-242\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The core points of the announcement emphasized were related to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>$20 Billion Investment In Arizona</li><li>Expansion of the Foundry Services</li><li>Plans to work on 7nm Meteor Lake in the second quarter of 2021</li><li>Showcasing of 7nm Intel&nbsp;Ponte Vecchio GPU</li><li>Progression of EUV Chip Fab Lithography manufacturing</li><li>In Q4 of 2021; Rebooting IDF Dubbed “Intel ON”</li><li>Collaboration for research with IBM</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The second most important announcement was IDM 2.0 (Integrated Device Manufacturer) for Intel’s design and manufacturing. The CEO has unveiled a manufacturing and business strategy to achieve the company goals comprising of three parts;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><strong>In-house manufacturing</strong> which will help with the design and production of the Intel chips</li><li>An <strong>expanded use of external foundries </strong>by leveraging partners like TSMC, Samsung, and GlobalFoundries, which will be beneficial in the manufacturing of products that are at the core of Intel’s computing services. This will take place in 2024 and will be for the consumer as well as the enterprise chips.&nbsp;</li><li>Intel Foundry Services is a stand-alone foundry business unit and the newly announced <strong>Intel Foundry Services provider</strong> responsible for manufacturing chips like x86, Arm, and RISC-V core chips for external clients who use Intel’s manufacturing technology. The competitive advantage that Intel has over its competitors is the location of these foundries, i.e. in the US and Europe, which will work for the government.</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Efficient Leadership with effective results:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The change of the company’s CEO from Bob Swan to Pat Gelsinger signals its focus on technological advancement as the new CEO is the inventor of the Intel 80486 processor. Although Swan was an important stabilizing force in the company, the process leadership of Gelsinger is the need of the hour as he is passionate about technology and considers himself a “geek”. His homecoming signals Intel’s comeback to its core competencies and strengths. Intel stands firm on its commitment towards the expansion of the Intel Foundry Services (IFS) with specific customer partners like Qualcomm. Qualcomm has recently acquired Nuvia, which is a custom arm core development that is combined with leading-edge manufacturing. Gelsinger, with his go-getter attitude, was quick to analyze Qualcomm’s plans and cash-in on them.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Intel is pretty much clear on its direction as the deliverables are distinct and they plan on addressing the areas where the company couldn’t make progress earlier/ has potential for growth, as Gelsinger quite openly admitted that the company was not able to ride on the EUV i.e. Extreme Ultraviolet Lithography execution, but now it plans on making progress towards it.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Intel announced to invest $20 billion in Two New Chip Factories', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Investment,Stockwatch', '1623071794_slejven-djurakovic-0uXzoEzYZ4I-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:16:34'),
(23, 'which-sexist-remarks-made-japan-s-25-billion-olympic-bet-pay-off', 'Mon, 29 Mar 2021 11:41:57 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yoshiro Mori, Japan’s former President of the Tokyo Olympics had to resign in February 2021 as his sexist comments on women were criticized and unwelcomed by the public all around the globe. This happened when was conducting summer games in Tokyo and enjoyed great fanfare, but because of the backlash he received on his remarks, the International Olympic Committee made him quit. His place was filled by Seiko Hashimoto who is a politician and has had the honor of being a seven-time Olympian.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mori’s Remarks -</strong> Japan has had major scandals pertaining to sexist ranting for the last 20 years.&nbsp; Mori’s remarks further sparked the controversy in the Japanese Olympic Committee (JOC) when he said that the female members “talk too much”. He should be applauded for causing a stir in the socially accepted norms and encouraging people, though unintentionally, to stand against them. Switzerland’s IOC officials got to know about it through corporate sponsor gender-advancement groups and prominent female athletes. Japanese were stirred to the point that led them to organize online petitions and boycott threats.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Let’s talk numbers! –</strong> The situation has also steered the lawmakers and corporate heads to insist that Tokyo join the UN convention, which will finally put an end to employment discrimination. Japan is losing $750 billion annually for not allowing women to participate in the workforce to showcase their full potential. As estimated by Goldman Sachs and other investment banks, Japan’s $5 trillion gross domestic product would get a&nbsp;15% boost&nbsp;by better utilizing female talent. Every study conducted in this regard points towards the benefits of accomplishing a vibrant and innovative environment if women are made a part of its workforce. A study comprising 1,069 leading firms across 35 countries and 24 industries was performed and found out that gender diversity resulted in more productive companies (as measured by market value and revenue).&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Japan falls 20 points on WEF -</strong> Under the government of Shinzo Abe, Japan fell 20 points on World Economic Forum’s gender-equality index and follows Saudi Arabia closely in female representation in parliament. Although Japan’s workforce female participation is now near 70% if looked upon closely, these jobs are “non-regular” and pay less. This was also prominent in the pandemic era, as the women bosses lost more jobs than their male counterparts.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japan’s&nbsp;Naoto Omi, president of the Labor Organization Rengo, encourages the bans discrimination between genders among employers based on sex, race, religion, and politics and endorses the International Labor Organization\'s Convention 111. He says: “Convention 111 is the international standard for banning discrimination; [Japan] will be seen as lacking a commitment to protect human rights. Mr.&nbsp;Mori\'s remarks are a testament to the lack of that commitment.”<strong>Japan to save $750 billion annually - </strong>Yoshiro Mori was an active participant in the debate that was going around in Tokyo regarding the ever-increasing price tag of the Olympics, valued at around $25 billion. However, if he has encouraged the public and the lawmakers to finally take a stand against the gender parity happening in the workforce, there might be a way to overlook these $25 billion. As of now, Japan is headed towards saving $750 billion each year if a prominent representation of women is done in the organizations!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Which Sexist remarks made Japan’s $25 billion Olympic Bet Pay Off?', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business', '1623071307_australian-coins-4952628_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:08:27'),
(24, 'flutter-considering-stock-listing-of-fanduel', 'Mon, 29 Mar 2021 11:46:29 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Flutter Entertainment plc is an Irish sports-betting company, comprising four sub-divisions; Flutter UK&amp;I, Flutter International, FanDuel Group, and Sportsbet. Rupert Murdoch, Chairman of Fox Corporation, has a stake of 2.6% in Flutter. Flutter ownership improved its ownership to 95% of FanDuel last year. It has made an agreement with Fox Corporation which gives Fox the right to acquire an 18.6% stake in the company. This option will be valid from June 2021. The division located in the US includes different brands like FanDuel, FOX Bet, TVG, PokerStars, and Betfair. This division is diverse in its operations in a way that it offers betting, both in retail and online, and caters to the betting of sports, online gaming, poker, television broadcasting as well as advance deposit betting on horse racing. It has established a name in its domain as a market leader. FanDuel was founded in 2009 and has been growing exponentially, due to which it has now become the largest online sports betting company claiming 40% of the market share. Flutter also spent $484 million in the US on sales and marketing, but the reported loss last year was $237 million.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":249,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-249\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Putting an end to the murmur</strong> - It was announced on March 15<sup>th</sup>, 2021 by Flutter Entertainment PLC that they were strategically considering some decisions for FanDuel company. This will include an Initial Public Offering in partial scholarship in the US. The company however clarified that no decision has yet been made but whenever that happens, it will be formally announced. Even this declaration benefited the company as its shares went up by 6%. The company plans on holding the remaining stake in FanDuel in order to grow as a global sports betting and gaming company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Rationale behind Exclusion</strong> – The stock market has been in-effective in assessing Flutter’s strong position in the market. This exclusion of Flutter from FanDuel is done in order to address this issue of undervaluation. According to the company, its revenues were higher than that of DraftKings, valued at $644 million, while Flutter was valued at $896 million. DraftKings entered the market in April 2020 through a merger with SPAC (Special Purpose Acquisition Company) in 2019, which was the closest rival to FanDuel. This merger was done at $10 per share. Flutter’s shareholders were not happy with the stock market as it failed to assess this strong market position. What’s interesting is that the announcement led to an increased share price of Flutter which was valued at 27.7 billion pounds ($38.5 billion). Separating Flutter from FanDuel will be useful to the shareholders as it will unlock its value and will provide an opportunity to the investors to finance in a market-leading US sports betting company. This will help diminish the adverse regulatory risk of flutter shares. As the States strive towards making online betting legal, the industry for online betting is also increasing. The Initial Public Offering could also provide a price discovery mechanism and maximize FOX’s option to acquire an 18.5% stake in FanDuel, priced to market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Flutter considering Stock-listing of FanDuel', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Uncategorized', '1623071346_iphone-472197_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:09:06'),
(25, 'usd-cad-move-towards-125-as-crude-oil-market-stabilises', 'Mon, 29 Mar 2021 12:47:31 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The combination of stronger Canadian sales and Crude oil stability has pushed the USDCAD pair higher than we expected. The USDCAD pair is currently trading close to the 1.25 mark and is expected to go up but a bearish trend is also inevitable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>USDCAD pair crossed 1.25 level and touched 1.2540 before declining back to 1.25 on Saturday. Experts had predicted a movement closer to this point which interestingly became a reality, thanks to Crude oil alone. USDCAD saw a 0.20% increase and became a red alert for the bears who had been trying to pull it back last week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":258,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/refinery-3400043_640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-258\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What happened last week?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>USDCAD had been under influence of the bears last week. In fact, on Thursday, it was hit hard when crude oil prices saw a sudden downfall. The journey has been quite rough for the pair and strong resistance levels were noticed at multiple instances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The beginning of last week predicted a down trend for USDCAD but as days passed by, the pair fought back to claim a higher position in the market. Later that week, crude oil prices helped the pair to break away from the strong bearish resistance and finally at the end of the week, we saw USDCAD rise way above the expected levels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Predicting the future</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The stabilisation of crude oil prices overtime has reduced the bearish pressure on the pair. WTI is currently approaching the $61 mark and might even cross during the next few days. Moreover, the retail performance in Canada has seen a boom in the month of January leading towards appreciation of the Canadian dollar against USD. This boom, however, was shortlived as FED\'s decision about supplementary leverage ratio was released later on.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Basically, FED decided to stop the extension of SLR during the pandemic. This allowed major US banks to hold back treasuries and deposits in order to exempt these from the capital requirement policies. As a result, initially, a rise in USD was seen which was later followed by an immense selling pressure on the US treasuries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The journey for USDCAD has been quite rough throughout the last 3 months but natural corrective measures are now expected soon enough. The pair pushed towards 1.2540 but declined back and has stayed that way since no new information has been released by Jerome Powell yet. A flat trend was noted last week but as we move towards the newer week, we can predict a positive outcome for the loonie traders.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Influenced by the statements of Toni, Deputy Governor Bank of Canada, the pair can take a turn at any point in time now.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Our verdict</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keeping in mind the historical data and the potential future trends, we are expecting USDCAD to rise in the long-term. The Canadian retail sales report has shown an optimistic outlook which is expected to grow but it should be kept in mind that the 3rd wave of global pandemic might bring things to a halt soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As of now, the USDCAD pair seems to be in control of the bulls but it won\'t be very smart to say that the bulls have complete control over it. The bears have been holding it back through a strong grip and might not let it slip away. Now is the time to sell the pair and gain a short term profit before buying it again at the end of this week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting content keep visiting our website and if you found this article helpful, don\'t forget to share it with your friends and family!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'USD/CAD move towards 125 as Crude oil market stabilises', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Economics', '1623071360_pexels-pixabay-162568.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:09:20'),
(26, 'usdchf-records-a-new-high-expected-to-cross-0-950-level', 'Tue, 06 Apr 2021 10:43:51 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The greenback had faced a lot of trouble during the previous weeks against all major currencies but the DXY has maintained its position and is now in a stronger position. The ripple effect of USD trading has made a serious impact on CHF and after 9 whole months, the USDCHF pair has set a new high record today.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The yields in United States are gradually losing the battle but surprisingly, DXY has managed to stay put 93.00 level which was not expected at all. The price movement has come as a shock to the investors and a bullish trend is now clearly visible to the naked eye!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":267,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/claudio-schwarz-purzlbaum-htol9OLeW20-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-267\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What\'s new with USDCHF?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The USDCHF pair had been on a flat track since yesterday but as the American Market opened today, the bulls kicked it hard and the pair went flying up towards its upper limit that was set back in July 2020. Soon, USDCHF was able to defeat the strong resistance levels that were set on 16th of July last year and it claimed its new high position at 0.9438 as the session began.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now USDCHF is successfully holding its position above 0.9400 and if the bears don\'t wake up soon, it will post the strongest close after 9 months of effort. If that happens, the trading trends would shift causing a ripple effect towards the rival pairs in Forex.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>USDCHF upwards trend - Secrets unveiled</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While the bulls are enjoying the strong upwards trend, the bears have only 1 question in mind:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Why is USDCHF moving up and where will the Bullish rule end eventually?</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Of course in a market like Forex there\'s no definite answer ever but a little analysis could take us to the root of this trend.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A strong motivator for this pair has been the greenback itself. The consistently increasing yields and USD has paved a way for USDCHF to go higher than anyone could\'ve expected. The 10 year yield set a new record at 1.77% on Tuesday and DXY decided to follow its path ending at 93.00 level for the first time since November 2020. As a result, USD got an edge over its rivals, specifically in the Eurozone and ended up higher at the end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the other hand, US stocks are facing a bearish resistance causing problems for the greenback. NASDAQ is currently -0.35% while DOW Jones is making a 0.13% dive. The consumer sentiment index, however, climed to a huge 109.70% compared to the predicted level of 96.9% which shows why we\'re currently standing at this point interms of the USDCHF pair.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The analysis above makes room for an overbought trend in which case the bulls are actually in deep trouble. The trend might go through a corrective movement which could push the pair to mid 0.93s level but having said that, at this point in time, USDCHF seems to be stronger than ever even with an overbought alarm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the pair breaks tha current resistance level and moves above 0.9430, a strong bullish wave is expected which might even push the pair above 0.960 towards the 0.970 mark.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Verdict</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Under the current circumstances it is recommended to buy USDCHF and wait for it to set its second new high record by the start of next week. However, chances of a corrective action are thin but real as well in which case the investors must keep an eye on the pair during the US trading hours. Anything below 0.9390 would be disastrous for the bulls and anything above 0.9430 would be a death warrant for the bears.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more helpful information, keep visiting our website and don\'t forget to share this article with your friends and family before you leave!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'USDCHF records a new high - Expected to cross 0.950 level', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currencies,Currency Market,Strategic Financial Management', NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 09:14:12'),
(27, 'gbpusd-ready-for-a-new-bearish-trip-as-us-job-reports-unveil', 'Tue, 06 Apr 2021 10:52:43 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GBPUSD\'s bullish journey finally came to an end on Friday and the pair is set to begin a bearish journey in the coming weeks. Joe Biden has been taking necessary measures to improve the economy of United States and surprisingly, he has been quite successful in his attempts. The economic outlook of USA has changed over the past few weeks and the nation is ready to rise again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Covid19 has been a global villain since December 2019. The ripple effect created by the pandemic is still noticeable in all major economies. USA, for instance, faced increased unemployment, inflation, dollar depreciation and increased developmental problems. These problems caused the greenback to fall during the early days of the global pandemic but now as we move on towards the mid of 2021, economies have started improving after a long tough fight with the villain itself and patterns in forex have started to change as a result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The GBPUSD pair which has been under bullish influence since the last few weeks is now looking at a bearish outlook and is expected to fall in the coming weeks. This prediction turned into reality on Friday.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":276,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/christopher-bill-rrTRZdCu7No-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-276\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>GBPUSD current outlook</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The two strongest economies fought throughout the week and on Friday GBPUSD faced minor losses that caught attention of investors throughout the globe. The latest NFP data release proved to be very beneficial for the US economy and as a result the DXY index moved just above the 93.00 mark. DXY has been moving around this mark since last week and just 2 days ago, it fell below 93.00 mark which is an important point to note here in order to analyse the future trends accurately.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Moreover, the 10 year US treasury bond yield which had fallen to a new low on Thursday successfully bounced back on Friday causing a shift in the ongoing GBPUSD bullish trend. The pair saw a downturn and went to its day\'s lowest at 1.3814 level before recovering back to 1.3820 mark. Interesting, even after the rebound, the GBPUSD pair was still in loss by a minor 0.08%. This sudden change of events have raised the bearish alarms and the bulls are now ready to support the pair.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>DXY expected to go above 93.00</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>DXY is currently hanging around the 93.00 level and is expected to close above this level by the end if this week. The US bureau of labor statistics report further added support to DXY levels when it revealed a total of 916000 nonfarm payrolls instead of the predicted level of 647000. In addition to these positive statistics, the publication details revealed a decline in the unemployment rates to 6% which further put pressure on the GBPUSD pair but to net it out a negative aspect was noticed. The average hourly earnings dropped to 4.2% from a previous 5.2% level.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Furthermore, the US treasury bond yield cleared out the negative pressure of Thursday and ended up above 1.1720% on Friday. As a result of these 3 developments, USD unexpectedly outperformed its rival currencies and a major appreciation was noticed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Final words</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The improvement noticed in the US economy along with a decline in GBP, the GBPUSD pair is pointing towards a shortterm bearish trend. The pair is expect to go below the current support levels before rising back up again. We recommend you to sell the pair now before buying it again at the end of next week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting articles, keep visiting our website and don\'t forget to share this article with your friends and family before leaving!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'GBPUSD ready for a new bearish trip as US job reports unveil', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currencies,Currency Market,Don\'t Miss,Investment', NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 09:14:12'),
(28, 'boost-in-wireless-technology-and-online-payments', 'Tue, 06 Apr 2021 11:22:05 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The internet has now become a major part of our lives and it is evolving every passing day. With the developments in digital and network technologies, Wi-Fi is becoming smarter and more advanced. According to recent <a href=\"https://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/solutions/executive-perspectives/annual-internet-report/air-highlights.html\">research conducted by Cisco</a>, each individual is expected to own, on average, four internet-connected devices by the year 2023, which was two in 2018.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since the pandemic hit globally in the year 2019, one of the biggest technological problems faced was the super sluggish unreliable internet connections because of the heavy traffic rate on the broadband providers. While this became the cause of a lot of problems on the whole, in the bigger picture, it led companies to become more concerned about the improvement of Wireless technology, hence the conception of a wave of new internet routers with <strong>Wi-Fi 6-</strong> <strong>a brand new networking standard</strong>! With this upgrade, the focus like the previous version has taken a big turn towards the improvement in efficiency rather than speed, through bandwidth sharing across various devices. In order to understand this, consider a situation where, for example, you are at your house where each of your family members has their own set of smart devices; cellphones, laptops, game console, etc. connected to the internet network, consuming heavy data to download information or stream video. The Wi-Fi 6 divides the bandwidth among devices all at the same time instead of allowing one of them to eat up most of it.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":282,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/paul-mcgrath-YjWU8G4J9xI-unsplash-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-282\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>The role of Wifi technology for online payments post-pandemic:</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social distancing has hailed new contactless technologies for online payments through digital mobile applications and websites. In comparison to the last few years, the usability of Wifi technology for data streaming has increased, along with its use in video conferencing, etc.&nbsp; Wireless technology, therefore, plays a vital role as an engagement channel for the distribution of diverse services as it helps to connect by making businesses accessible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A survey conducted by the <a href=\"https://www.retailcustomerexperience.com/news/covid-19-driving-contactless-card-use-mobile-payments-despite-security-cost-worries/\">National Retail Federation and Forrester</a> showed that people preferred using online wallets using QR codes for online payments; “67% of retailers surveyed accept some form of no-touch payment, and that includes 58% that accept contactless cards that can be waved past a card reader or tapped on the reader. That figure is up from 40% last year. ”&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>QR codes at checkouts were integrated by <strong>Paypal in </strong>CVS Pharmacies, <strong>Walmart</strong>&nbsp;introduced&nbsp;online payment options with contact-free pickup and delivery services in March 2020, <strong>Line Pay</strong> collaborated with Tokyo Gas in Japan to exercise online payment procedures.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Trends of Global Wireless Technology Market</strong>:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While all other sectors got hit drastically by the Coronavirus, the only sector that seems to have been positively influenced was the Information technology and Telecom segment. The rate at which the wireless infrastructure is being implemented globally, the market value is anticipated to see healthy growth in the coming years; i.e. from $ 69.44 billion in 2016 to $53.17 billion in 2019 to a high growth spike expected to $150.38 billion at CAGR of 13% by the year 2027. The telecom sector is projected to be crowned with this progression owing to the evolution of the applications of Wireless technology in cloud computing, BYOD, IoT, WYOD, and Artificial Intelligence, etc.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Boost in Wireless Technology and Online Payments', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Uncategorized', NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 09:14:12'),
(29, 'bitcoin-crosses-60000-next-target-100000', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 16:01:40 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bitcoin saw a major spike yesterday, 14th March 2021 and investors are very excited about it. The king of all crypto, Bitcoin has been setting new records for a long time now. A journey that began within the 10k region and ended up above 50k has made it a very popular trade throughout the globe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The question here is, how long will bitcoin\'s bullish moves survive? Well, right now as we write, bitcoin is under the influence of the bears but the long term analysis shows a clear bullish trend that might end anywhere between $100000 and $200000. Having said that, the journey won\'t be that easy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cryptocurrency is known for risk. Investing in cryptocurrency for longer time periods is like gambling, you might double your savings or even lose it all!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":226,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/dmitry-demidko-OG3A-ilG8AY-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-226\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Bitcoin crosses $60000 mark</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite pessimistic opinions of many experts, Bitcoin managed to cross the $60k mark and the king sent out a clear message:&nbsp;<em>There\'s no stopping now!</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The bears haven\'t been successful in pulling it back however, today the bears are quite active but that won\'t last long. Bitcoin touched the new high of $61699 on March 14 2021 and previously it had tested the $62000 resistance level. The journey of bitcoin is set towards the 100k mark but it would face strong resistance throughout. Here\'s our prediction for BTC:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Level 1: Bitcoin passes $62000.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Level 2: Bitcoin reaches $75000 but strong resistance pulls it back under $70k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Level 3: Bitcoin breaks this resistance level and touches $100k before declining back into the $90000s level.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Level 4: Bitcoin crosses the $100k mark.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While these predictions are not a reality yet, the next 30 days are quite crucial for BTC. We have analysed the past trends and come with potential future trends and that is how the bigger picture looks like.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What will happen in the next 7 days?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While all indicators had shown a positive push for BTC, many investors have lost their investments as the fluctuation continues to grow. If Bitcoin breaks the resistance level at $62000, we will definitely see a new record high price within the $70000s level.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unfortunately, that hasn\'t been the case today. Instead, the bears have taken control of the market today and BTC has fallen by a huge gap of $4000 resulting in a liquidation of billions of dollars. Right now the current BTCUSD pair stands at&nbsp; $56100 (March 15, 2021) and it is expected to decline further before rising up again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Eventually, the bulls are expected to get away with the victory but the bears would prove to be very damaging during this competition. The huge fluctuations in the BTCUSD pair make it very risky and in the past these fluctuations have also created a gap of up to $11000 which has resulted in a loss of billions of dollars.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To sum it up, Bitcoin has a strong future ahead but it would be challenged by the bears throughout. If you\'re a small investor with a limited investment and your plans are to play in a risk aversive style, do not invest all your resources in BTC as the fluctuations could lead to bankruptcy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the other hand, if you\'re a big investor with a diversified portfolio, buy some BTC now and who knows you might double or even triple your equity in the coming months!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting news related to the financial market, keep visiting our website. Don\'t forget to share this article with your friends and family!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Bitcoin crosses $60000, Next target $100000', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Hot Updates,Uncategorized', '1623071260_euro-5094279_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:07:40'),
(30, 'eurjpy-under-influence-of-the-bulls-expected-price-level-to-go-beyond-138', 'Mon, 22 Mar 2021 16:40:38 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The EURJPY pair continues to experience a bullish trend traveling towards the end of the week. The EURJPY pair was previously under strong control of the bears and the outlook had seemed to be very pessimistic overall. The pair was seen going down but in an interesting turn of events, EURJPY bounced back earlier this week and is now set to cross the 130 mark.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While EURJPY has been fighting hard to break through the strong resistance levels around 130, bears have been trying to make a comeback every day. The question to be highlighted here is:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Where exactly is EURJPY heading and what move is the best at this point in time?</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Facing two strong pullbacks today, EURJPY has continued its upside journey and the next upside is expected at around 130.50 level. Will EURJPY break this boundary? Or will it fall back in the bear trap?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":229,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://summitstocks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/markus-spiske-ms6N-gBtbCQ-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-229\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>EURJPY complete analysis</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The pair has been on a tough journey since a long time now but our analysis predicts an optimistic outlook in the future. EURJPY is expected to cross the 130 region any day now and if that happens, a new high of 132 can be expected soon enough. The pair will see strong resistance around this level but breaking it would mean a new record high price that has never been seen before.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interestingly, EURJPY has been trading above the support level, 127.50, that was naturally created back in November 2020. The strong support in this region has allowed the pair to maintain its dominance over the bears on and off.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The broader look or the bigger picture right now shows a constant upside trend for the next few weeks but it won\'t come without a fight from the bears. If bulls are successful in defeating the short bearish pullbacks, EURJPY might touch the 140 level in the coming month. Now this is something that wasn\'t expected at all!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Upcoming Important levels for EURJPY</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As the pair pushes towards the new highs of the week, resistant forces are acting up to weaken the bullish mechanism. For the coming week, certain EURJPY levels would be very important to note for investors who are looking to invest short-term and long term. Right now the pair has gained about 0.22% around the 130 mark and is continuing to rise. Here are the levels to be noted next week:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. A strong hurdle is expected at 130.50 which would help the bears take control of the situation to some extent but good news for the bulls, it won\'t last long and the pair is definitely expected to cross this mark.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. The next important level would be 131 but this has to do with the psychological factors. When EURJPY touches 131, the cognitive abilities of many investors would push them to sell the pair creating an illusion that it might be overbought. Of course, that won\'t last long either.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. If EURJPY crosses the first 2 levels, the 3rd level would be the high of 2018 around 131.98. Here things would get interesting. A strong resistance is expected at 131.98 but if EURJPY crosses this point, there\'s not stopping it then!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Our verdict:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While EURJPY is on a bullish journey this week, the scenario might take a 180 degrees turn and go in favour of the bears for a short time period but that won\'t be easy. Currently, favouring a bearish trend for EURJPY would be quite unrealistic. The pair is set to cross 140 and it might even make a new world record.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The only important aspect to be noticed here is the fluctuation that would occur during the next few weeks. If traded smartly, the losses can be minimised and huge gains can be expected.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep visiting us for more interesting content and don\'t forget to share this article before leaving!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'EURJPY Under influence of the bulls, expected price level to go beyond 138', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Currencies,Currency Market', '1623071235_iphone-472197_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 08:07:15');
