(53, 'the-uk-all-set-to-introduce-britcoin-a-new-digital-currency', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 11:53:15 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The hype of digital currency in the world started back in the year 2013 when crypto-currencies were newly introduced. From Bitcoin to Lite coin, and then to Etherium; all these were introduced in the global stock market. Initially, the value of the cryptocurrencies was declining as the investors were afraid to put their hands into this new market buzz. The initial price of bitcoin in 2013 was near $67.18; which started to increase slowly and gradually as more currencies were introduced in the market. Afterwards, with the initiation of mining of these currencies through various platforms, the digital currency also started to gain popularity among people and emerged in the world with a boom. Now, out of all the thousands of currencies that were introduced in the past, Bitcoin has been lucky enough to flourish enough to achieve double thousand figures, valuating at about $ 10,000 to nearly $ 50,000.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Journey of Bitcoin to Britcoin:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Within the last 3 to 4 years, Bitcoin has gained so much popularity that every country has accepted these digital currencies and has been making use of them, instead of the normal note currency. They have played a significant role in boosting each country’s economy; the main reason of which being the conversion of currencies i.e. from Dollars to each country’s local currency, since the dollar is considered as a stable currency all across the globe.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taking into account the massive gain and success of bitcoin across the world, British Finance Minister Rishi Sunak asked the Governor of the Bank of England to look into this matter and launch a new cryptocurrency, as soon as possible. The finance minister further told that this currency should emerge as a strong contender to the leading cryptocurrencies. A management team has been put into place, acting as a middle-man between the treasury and the members of BoE for settlement of a stable currency for all the customers. The finance minister further elaborated that after launching Britcoin, other banks of England will also start working on these digital currencies once the first team starts receiving at least 0.1% of the success rate. It has also been clarified that this new currency will not replace the Pounds, or any other currency but this will be an addition to the list of existing currencies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Blocking Dark Trading</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The finance minister further told the governor of BoE that due to the Brexit of the UK from the European Union, it has suffered a major setback to their financial sector and the loss they had to bear was mainly because of the restrictions imposed on them by the European Union. With this issue escalating, dark trading became evident in the European sector and every second person started to become a victim. Hence, the production of Britcoin, it is envisioned that the sanctions that have been imposed might be reduced and it will be a new venture that can globally get accepted. Furthermore, all the dark and anonymous investors will gain prominence which will finally bring an end to their all-black crimes, leading to the opening up of new ventures for investments, and the market will flourish more. The overall advantages will be visible in all the financial sectors which will help Britain in winning back its lost economy.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The UK all set to Introduce BritCoin! – a New Digital Currency', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Crypto Apps,Hot Updates', '1623070428_euro-5094279_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:53:48'),
(54, 'fatal-car-crash-crashes-tesla-stocks', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:30:45 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This week’s Saturday, the news of one of Tesla’s car crash got aired, that carried two passengers aged 59 and 69 who had reportedly been driving on auto-pilot mode. The car was going at a high speed on a sharp turn; with one passenger sitting in the front passenger seat and the other in the back seat, when it went off the road at a distance of about 100 feet, hit a tree and ended up turning into massive flames. The fire which usually takes minutes to extinguish took about four long hours for the fire brigade to put down. This car crash brings Tesla’s ‘autopilot car crashes’ to a total of more than a dozen, recorded in just the past month. The main reason for the mishaps is probably the batteries used in these Tesla vehicles that are believed to be unstable, causing ‘thermal runway’ at high speeds, resulting in ‘uncontrolled contact’ within different materials used in the batteries. The National Highway Transportation Safety Administration has taken charge of the investigations and follow-up reports shall be shared later.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Is Tesla 2019 Model S a safe vehicle?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since the spread of the car crash news, the PR team of Tesla has refused to comment on the incident which has caused more people to seriously question whether or not we have reached that level of futuristic technology to let self-driving cars out on the roads with other traffic. In the past year 2016, we saw another Tesla self-driven vehicle (Model S) crash after failing to apply brakes for a tractor and turned in front of it instead.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tesla techno-king and imperator of Mars, Elon Musk <a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1383548841438236674?s=20\">released a report</a> claiming that “Tesla with Autopilot engaged now approaching 10 times lower chance of accident than the average vehicle.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, 23 recent accidents have brought Tesla’s futuristic goals under fresh scrutiny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>With Tesla crashing, are the stocks getting affected as well?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, the incident has added to the distrust around self-driven cars in people due to which Tesla witnesses the lowest of lows this month over the weekend. First, the stocks experienced a drop to as low as 6.5% in New York, then things got tenser as the National Highway Transportation Safety Administration announced to launch an investigation against more than a dozen Tesla vehicles running on auto-pilot mode.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Saturday’s car crash triggered a domino effect of bad news into the market; EV start-ups are facing a threat of losing investment as market behemoths are ready to roll out new models of Mercedes-Benz AG and Stellantis NV. On the brighter side, however, the 94-year-old company; Mercedes-Benz, has introduced its first all-electric vehicle and is also ready to sell it all across the United States, while Ferrari NV plans to introduce its vehicle in the year 2025.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Another major automobile manufacturing company (like General Motors Co., Ford Motor Co., and Volkswagen AG) followed this news with the announcement of introducing their electric vehicles into the market this year. This shows that time is running out for Musk to exercise the necessary remedial measures as EV start-ups and other competitors are bringing a safer self-driven automobile out in the marketplace.&nbsp;&nbsp;Bloomberg analyst, Kevin Tynan, released a report on April 14 where he made out a comparison between 2019 and 2020 sales of Tesla’s battery-driven cars and pointed out a slip of 1 percentage point to 24%. On the other hand, “the share of the VW Group <a href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eaf-stock-buy-sell-192228196.html\">rose to 9% from 4%</a> in 2019, on track to overtake Tesla in 2023 and a sign that established automakers may quickly gain once committed to the drivetrain technology.”&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'FATAL CAR CRASH CRASHES TESLA STOCKS', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Hot Updates,Stockwatch', '1623070412_vlad-tchompalov-jwyO3NhPZKQ-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:53:32'),
(55, 'cryptocurrencies-soon-to-be-available-on-venmo', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:33:54 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The new buzz in the world of finance and marketing nowadays is cryptocurrency! Every individual is in the rush to invest in cryptocurrency making it the new enigma trending across the globe. This does not only include hype about the most expensive cryptocurrency- Bitcoin, but various other currencies are making their way to the top these days. From Bitcoin to Ethereum to Lite Coin, all these currencies are gaining publicity and their market value is increasing from $11 per coin to $ 2,200 per coin. Therefore, getting your hands onto cryptocurrency was not an easy job in the past. People had to go through the whole procedure that includes various bank transactions through multiple platforms like Binance, Coinbase, Gemini, etc. However, in recent times, this method has also been eased up for the users through the introduction of a new platform- VENMO!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Venmo making it all possible</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is one of the biggest platforms now serving as the availability ground for all cryptocurrencies. According to various confirmed resources like Reuters, all the trading can now be easily performed; buying, selling, and holding on all the coins in various platforms via Venmo. There are more than 70 million users on this platform and they will all be eligible to avail of this facility. Venmo is the second most famous money transfer application after PayPal, which has introduced this feature for its customers through an application. It facilitates the customers for increasing their digital assets most conveniently. In the initial phase, there will only be four cryptocurrencies available for the customers on the feed that includes <strong>BitCoin, Litecoin, Ethereum, and Bitcoin Cash,</strong> as they are the most trending coins all across the globe. The GM of Venmo at PayPal states that it will be a fun-based journey for the consumers to utilize this facility.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Availability of features and net profit:</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The application started working on this venture around 2020 when the Corona pandemic struck the countries and their economies started to face a major downfall. With the increasing rate of unemployment, as high as 5million people were reported to be desperately looking for investment opportunities and platforms where they can capitalize their assets to gain maximum profits. At that time, Venmo started buying the coin base and about 30% of the shares are now readily available. The profit gained by Venmo through cryptocurrencies will increase their global market shares from $20 billion per year. This feature will further move to PayPal, thus allowing PayPal customers to get the benefits as well. At the moment, the application is not allowing the customers to shop through cryptocurrencies, however; PayPal has given access to its US-based customers so that they can shop through local and global vendors who deal in cryptocurrency. The General Manager of Venom explained that the application will provide a proper guide, statistics, and growth chart to monitor all the updates regarding the cryptocurrencies so that the customers remain totally satisfied.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Cryptocurrencies soon to be available on Venmo', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Crypto Mining News,Hot Updates,Our Story', '1623070401_tech-daily-UODNyThs0vg-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:53:21'),
(56, 'amazon-announces-new-payment-method-at-some-stores', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:37:20 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is 2021- the future is near, if not here! Amazon is in the news again for another innovative idea brought to fruition. You have heard of paying with cash, by debit card, credit card, scanning QR codes, wire transfers, online transfers, and even small change. Are you familiar with paying through the palm of your hand? That’s right! Your unique handprint can become a source of making payments at some whole food stores in the US now. Amazon One is another service provided by the behemoth company, Amazon Inc. It allows customers to connect their credit cards or Amazon accounts with the palm of their hands. The world of carrying wallets is becoming an obsolete one as this new technology is activated at a few whole food grocery stores located near the Amazon HQ in the states. All customers have to do is scan their palms at the cashier counter and make payments. This <strong>new technology by Amazon One</strong> is called <strong>pay-by-palm technology</strong>. Amazon claims the setup takes less than a minute!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Pay-by-hand technology launched last year:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2021 is not the year of this payment method’s birth. It arrived in 2020, launched by Amazon obviously. Scanning palms for making payments could be conveniently used at stadiums, some retailers, and selected office buildings. Amazon promises to have signed up thousands of customers for this innovative payment technology, however, they haven’t released the exact number.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Boon or bane?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It could be interesting to imagine a world where nobody will carry tangible paper cash and walk around with just their hands in their pockets! Pun intended. On the other hand, one cannot help but wonder about financial management. In this constantly growing mammoth of the capitalist world, how will a customer restrain themselves from making unnecessary purchases, knowing that it’s all just at their arm’s length! Yes, another pun intended. This could mean good news for businesses, bad news for shopaholics and foodies. One thing is for sure… your friend will never arrive at a dinner empty-handed!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apart from financial management, another risk arises; i.e. Security. While China is leading the firewall technology when it comes to digital banking, is the USA ready for such a leap in their e-payments? USA and China are the leading competitors in the market, undoubtedly. With China becoming the first country to mainstream their digital currency e-yuan, is this USA’s way of bringing the competition up a notch? Experts are also skeptical about using biometric data to make payments. Biometric data is notorious to get hacked or stolen, especially in the USA. Amazon defends this critique by claiming that images of unique palm prints are stored in a secure cloud and stores are obliged to delete data upon customer’s request. The individual information is not stored in the Amazon One device either.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nonetheless, this is an exciting development of the century you and I are living in. Forget about muggers, pickpockets… however, I guess you better beware of the palmists now!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Amazon announces new payment method at some stores', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Crypto Mining News,Currency Market,Stockwatch', '1623070379_bryan-angelo-FtiXADBTqGY-unsplash-1.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:52:59'),
(57, 'recession-covid-19-may-eat-up-japan-s-livelihood', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:51:39 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japan, like many other countries, is not coping well with the coronavirus pandemic. The Japanese economy and people’s Golden Week celebration depend on a decision which is expected to be taken by the government soon. Repeated state of emergency imposed in Japan to contain the spread of the virus will hit the economy very hard and the slow rollout of vaccine is not making the situation any easier. Keep in mind that Tokyo is set to host the Olympics in July, but experts are already casting a shadow of doubt on whether it’s logistically possible to hold a mega international event. Nonetheless, Prime Minister Yoshihide Suga is positive that the biggest athletic event will take place at the scheduled time despite a year delay already. Another major event had to be canceled due to the pandemic. Japan was set to host Tokyo Motor Show, but an announcement of ‘difficulties in holding the show’ made by Japan Automobile Manufacturers Association Chairman Akio Toyoda brought down enthusiasts’ spirits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All this bad news is followed by experts and analysts in words as, “The risk of a double-dip recession has clearly heightened,” said Hiroshi Shiraishi, a senior economist at BNP Paribas Securities.&nbsp;Fears of consequences following locking down Osaka and Tokyo are showing evidently.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Covid situation in Japan:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not only the new strain of coronavirus is wreaking havoc in Japan, but the government’s mismanagement of vaccine distributing is resulting in an increasing number of cases daily. With a 7-day average of 4509 cases, a decision is on its way to lock down major cities as soon as next week. Compared to the number of cases in January with April, there is an alarming difference of more than hundreds of cases. The highest number of cases recorded in January was 4928, whereas a record number of 5396 cases are recorded in April.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Four regions of Japan have reportedly requested the government to declare emergency measures. If Prime Minister Suga agrees, the lockdown would cover almost a quarter of Japan’s population (which is 126 million) and about 30 percent of the gross domestic product. A Japanese news agency reported the duration of the state of emergency will last from 25 April to 11 May. This would mean a cultural celebration of Golden Week will be affected.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to Economy Minister Yasutoshi Nishimura, Japan needs to take stronger and more targeted steps before closing down departmental and other wholefood stores.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Celebrations hampered:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Requests of imposing emergency measures could not have come at a worse time for locals. Golden Week is right around the corner which means retailers and small business owners have the chance to earn maximum profit and contribute to the Japanese economy. Takumi Tsunoda- the Japanese senior economist agrees that timing is bad and he <a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2021/4/22/double-dip-japan-risks-recession-if-new-covid-emergency-declared\">forecasted</a> that in the second-quarter of this year, the GDP growth will see a 0.5 percent quarter-on-quarter rise. This makes it half the previously projected rapidity. This could affect the Bank of Japan’s quarterly growth projections report expected to release next week. Lockdown, if decided, will last all through Golden Week celebrations.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Recession: Covid-19 may eat up Japan’s livelihood', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Economics', '1623070366_amy-tran-LFHUJYJceQ-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:52:46'),
(58, 'audusd-climb-to-0-7750-as-dxy-continues-to-fall', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:59:29 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The AUDUSD pair decided to turn 180° towards north as the trading hours began earlier today. The pair that had been fighting to get a breakthrough since last week is now finally under the bullish shadows. The bulls are pushing it upwards and the bears don\'t know what to do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Will this be another bear trap? Or is AUDUSD actually under a longterm bullish influence? Let\'s find out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The story</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After losing badly on Tuesday, the AUDUSD pair went crashing down to 0.7700 level and was expected to decline even further during the American session on Wednesday. However, fate had written the opposite of what every investor had expected and in matter of seconds, the odds turned in favor of the bulls which resulted in a sudden upward move for the AUDUSD pair. The rebound came at 0.7700 level and it was successful in netting out the negative effects of the previous day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A major reason behind this unexpected phenomenon was the depreciation of DXY which pulled it down to 91.00 level earlier today. While investors were gaining confidence in the US dollar, the index turned out to be a huge disappointment and as a result changed the scenario completely. Tge falling US dollar index was later met with an improve in the Australian economy. The market Sentiment showed positive results in Australia just as USD was going dark and as a result, the pressure on the greenback doubled. Unfortunately, the greenback failed to handle this pressure and gave up against AUD which caused a sudden spike in the AUDUSD pair.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is interesting to note that previously, the pair was deeply influenced by the bears and had reached its lowest point around 0.7698. The predicted trends along with various analysis tools showed a selling trend in the current week but the rebound today during the American session has pushed AUDUSD to a new high record at 0.7762 level. Experts are now predicting a journey towards 0.78 but that would ring the overbought alarm and the pair would face a corrective action as a result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Moreover, Gold reached the $1800 mark and the 10 year US treasury yields maintained at 1.56% causing a great impact on the pair. In addition to this, the Wall Street report showed an improvement in the market with DOW gaining 0.55% and NASDAQ 0.61%. These stats became a key driver for the pair and their influence is expected to remain for at least the next 3 trading days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The next major movement is expected tomorrow, on Thursday when Australia will reveal its latest report on the Australian Bank Business Confidence and USA will reveal its latest findings on Home Sales and Jobs report.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pandemic has caused major economies to fail and right now, the US economy is one of them. The expected Jobs report is not very positive at the moment and an increased unemployment or failure to reach the target percentage is expected in USA whereas, Australian economic report is expected to boost the investor confidence tomorrow morning which would result in a continued bullish trend.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you found this article helpful, don\'t forget to share it with your friends and family. Help us grow!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'AUDUSD climb to 0.7750 as DXY continues to fall', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Crypto Mining News,Currency Market', '1623070348_australian-coins-4952628_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:52:28'),
(59, 'eurusd-back-under-the-bearish-influence-as-dxy-appreciates', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 21:40:02 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The greenback has been fighting to gain a competitive position in the market since last week and it would be realistic to say that it has list big time against its rival currencies. However, things took a sharp turn today as DXY started exhibiting signs of positivity and greenback managed to take advantage of it, helping itself towards a more northern side of the trade. Previously on Summitstocks, our analytical report showed how DXY was expected to fall which would cause a bullish movement for the AUDUSD pair but today at the peak of trading hours, DXY stood up for itself and started moving in the opposite direction.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The only question that arises in such scenario is:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>How long would DXY compete before failing again?</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As of now, there is no definite answer to this question but after an in-depth analysis we came to the conclusion that DXY\'s upward journey is short-term and so is EURUSD\'s bearish trend. Here\'s why:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>EURUSD Drop Analysis</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The EURUSD pair gained momentum as the trading hours began earlier today. During the American session, a selling pressure was noticed which resulted in favorable bearish conditions. DXY moved from 91.00 to 91.35 level while EURUSD pair which was previously at a high of 1.2070 fell sharply towards the 1.20 level. A major reason behind the DXY improvement was a positivity in the US treasury yields that was revealed during the American session today which showed a higher position compared to what we saw last week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These changed caused the pair to crash towards South and bears were waiting impatiently to welcome their new guest. Bulls on the other hand tried to support the pair on various instances but the strong bearish conditions caused a complete failure. The pair is right now facing a new daily low and investors are slowly losing confidence which rings a medium term bearish alarm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is, however, interesting to note that EURUSD saw a sudden spike during the European session when Central Bank of Europe held a press conference to reveal the latest revelations. ING analysts highlighted how the outputs revealed during the press conference were in line with the predictions made.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“The phasing out of PEPP purchases was not discussed, and the exchange rate comments did not stand out. The euro&nbsp;sailed through the meeting unaffected, and the focus now turns to the expected improvement in Eurozone&nbsp;data, which should help to&nbsp;push the undervalued EUR/USD higher this quarter”. - FXS</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While this was the case in Europe, EUR managed to maintain its position despite less promising results. However, in USA the scenario was quite different. The unemployment report revealed a betterment in the US economy as the jobless claims fell to 547000 mark. On the other hand, a slightly negative pullback was also seen in terms of the housing program. The sales of existing houses fell by 3.7% last month while the predicted output was actually a net increase. The 10 year US treasury bond stands at 1.58% as of now and the greenback is expected to appreciate for tbe next two trading days which would cause a stronger bearish trend for EURUSD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting content, keep visiting our website and don\'t forget ti subscribe before leaving!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'EURUSD back under the bearish influence as DXY appreciates', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currency Market,Don\'t Miss', '1623070337_pexels-karolina-grabowska-4968666.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:52:17'),
(60, 'xauusd-crashes-towards-the-south-bears-dominating-the-bulls', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 21:42:43 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;XAUUSD\'s bullish journey finally came to an end earlier today. The pair had been under strong bullish influence since the last few weeks and it set a new monthly high record at $1800 mark before getting trapped by the bears again. Gold has been living dangerously since the beginning of this year and has faced many obstacles, sometimes in form of yields ans at other times in form of cryptocurrency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While many experts had predicted bitcoin to become a permanent Gold replacement and many companies like Tesla and Mastercard took interest in the king of metals, Gold managed to claim a strong position in the market. However, a large amount of investment in cryptocurrencies lead to decreased investment in Gold which again caused difficulties for the yellow metal. Interestingly, the same trends have started to repeat but this time Cryptocurrency is not a major reason behind the decline if Gold, US treasury yield is the real villain.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How bears took control?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>XAUUSD reached the 1800 dollar mark and was aiming towards the 1850 level but certain developments in the US economy pulled back the pair and it came crashing down back to the 1700s levels. The US treasury bond yield climbed up by 2% during the American session today and the DXY has been showing signs of improvement as well. In addition to this, the latest PMI report on the USA revealed stronger price pressure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All these developments made a strong impact on Gold and the mechanism that was once showing a positive future outlook is now under shadows of a pessimistic approach. During the beginning trading hours today, Gold reached its highest $1795 before running through a defence mechanism that pulled it back to the $1778 level. Right now XAUUSD is currently trading at a loss of 0.3% and this figure is expected to grow next week.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The rebound made by the US treasury yield has put pressure on Gold. The current benchmark for US treasury yield is now set at 2%. Moreover, IHS Markit revealed its latest data which drew a positive picture of the US economy. According to IHS, the private sector in the USA expanded by a huge margin and the pace at which it is continuing to expand is being considered as a new record. The index has risen from 59.7 to 62.2 while the predicted point was around 61 mark. However, an important point to be noted here is that producers within the USA have been passing on the price increases to the consumers which might become a cause of future inflation and reverse the current market mechanisms that are in favor of the greenback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The XAUUSD pair was further kicked out of sight after revelation of the latest housing program data which showed that home sales increased to 20.7% which was way more than the predicted 12.8%. However, the DXY is now expected to decline yet again which would cover the damages done to XAUUSD to some extent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The pair seems to be in deep trouble right now but the trouble we\'re talking about here is an opportunity for the bears to maximize their profits. In case of overselling, XAUUSD might face a corrective action which would boost it again but that won\'t turn into a reality very soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep visiting us for more interesting content and help us grow by sharing this article with your friends and family!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'XAUUSD crashes towards the South - Bears dominating the Bulls!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Currencies,Hot Updates,News &amp; Updates', '1623070328_alicia-razuri-mmHzeIV52ZI-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:52:08'),
(61, 'rolls-royce-in-profitable-conversations-with-spain', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 21:45:47 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rolls Royce is one of the finest automobile companies in the world, famous for its luxurious cars. The company is globally renowned among people for its amazing features and the driving ease it brings to its valuable customers. It is a UK-based brand that started its global production outside Great Britain. This first step took Rolls Royce to America, and then to Europe.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The constructive talks between Rolls Royce and the Spanish authorities were at a severe deadlock after Brexit in Feb 2020; however, now the situation is getting accommodative paving ways for talks between both parties, and may ultimately act as the ice breaker.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The margin of Business Profit</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is considered that Rolls Royce sees a great margin of profit and may acquire up to 1.5 billion Euros, equivalent to $1.8 billion from the sales point of view, which is all about the turbine maker blade of ITP aerospace. It is considered as one of the major essential parts from the trade perspective as well as through the business standpoint and may result in a high advantage rate in the overall business of the company. The ITC aerospace has a block sale of about 2 billion pounds which requires repair and has been getting delayed because of the pandemic lockdowns.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to several reports, it was assumed that they may experience a deadlock because of this issue since Munich was not in favor of supporting this business venture, however, soon afterward all these reports were eradicated by the Rolls Royce company statement that said that the headquarter of ITP is itself stated in the Basque region and that the ice breaker has worked out for them and they can work without any limitations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Spanish Companies and their Reservations</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since the deadlock problem got resolved, another question that popped up soon after that was all about the shares, the financial issues, and the situation both the parties may end up facing. The Spanish company insisted upon attaining sufficiently high shares for the mass production of IYC aerospace and the amount of steel that is required for such massive production. Hence, after major talks, the amount that got finalized in shares by Rolls Royce was about 1.7% at the 101 pence on 1356 GMT. This was to be accounted as the main amount decided at the beginning of the talks since the company had already recognized the buyers’ requirements in order to complete assurance before making any purchases.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The company further elaborated that in the month of December last year, the company faced a major setback that became the main reason for the loss of about $2.9 billion because of deadlock between the companies, but as soon as the deadlock got lifted, a boost of $1 million was observed in the market. This was the prime reason where the share price started getting higher. The company is quite hopeful that by the end of the deadlock time period, there will soon be a period of distinction when mass production will rapidly increase and result in a rapid boost to the country’s economy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Rolls Royce in Profitable Conversations with Spain', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Don\'t Miss', '1623069983_rolls-royce-2362821_1920.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:46:23'),
(62, 'samsung-leading-the-global-market-charts', 'Mon, 26 Apr 2021 21:49:27 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The world is full of a huge variety of cellular brands. The majority of these mobile companies run on Android-based software, despite this, iOS-based phones are still considered royalty and have always been at the top of the list. There has always been a big competition between the Android and iPhone users, arguing upon which phone has better specs and features leading on the charts. This never-ending war may never end, but the fact that Android mobiles always get an edge because of their diverse models and features may probably never be falsified.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to a recent survey conducted on the cellular market, the reports disclosed a very shocking result that highlighted that Apple is no more on the leading ends of the charts, as the first three slots were secured by android cellular brands; the first being Samsung, and the next two slots are filled by Xiaomi and OPPO, respectively.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Increased share in First quarter of the year</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A report recently shared in the global market by a cellular company states that in the first quarter of this year, the sales of the cellular devices have risen to 23%, which is record-breaking! The main reason for this increase in the sale is considered to be the launch of the new <strong>Samsung</strong> <strong>A</strong> <strong>series</strong>, equipped with 4g and 5g technology that has urged the tech-junkies to jump on the bandwagon. The company has already shipped nearly 77 million cellular phones globally, making it a record-breaking statistic. Taking into consideration such high sales, the technologists are estimating that Samsung will nearly reach 32% of the annual market share by the end of this year, marking as the highest market share by cellular companies since 2015; with a total average of all the smartphones sold out in the first quarter of the year reaching to around 340 million units. Samsung is, therefore, the biggest contributor in the market by far, with the maximum number of cellphones sold out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Market performance of other Brands</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to the director of the Strategy analysis, the overall contribution by other cellular companies was also commendable as they have been the side factors to bring the market position better. The cumulative efforts by Xiaomi and OPPO brought the rate to the point of the market. But the hot sellers in the market were <strong>Samsung\'s newly launched S21 and A series</strong> smartphones. In the survey conducted, the mobile spare parts and buying &amp; selling of cellular microchips were not included in the statistics but had an in-depth insight into all the cellphones which were bought that time across the globe. Another feature that came into observation unveiled that Xiaomi has been the leading cellular company in India and China but now it has also been successful at maintaining its position in Latin America, Africa, and various European countries. It is also anticipated that Xiaomi may take over the market in the coming years, with the availability of its unique features in a pocket-friendly range, staging a big threat to tech giant- Samsung.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Samsung leading the Global market charts', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Hot Updates', '1623069973_pexels-omar-markhieh-1447254.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:46:13'),
(63, 'gogoro-all-set-to-enter-asian-market', 'Tue, 04 May 2021 11:34:50 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gogoro is not a new name in the automobile industry; it is one of the top-notch and leading brands well-known around the world. People rely on this brand blindly because of their quality and high power maintenance of vehicles, along with their battery timings and efficiency. Gogoro was initially famous in Taiwan and China, but with time, their export increased in Europe and America, and now it is considered a global brand. The new venture of this company is that they are now entering the South East Asian countries. Gogoro is all set to launch their outlet in India, with the collaboration of Hero Group.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to sources, the net worth of the Gogoro group in 2019 was about USD 32.5 billion, estimated to have increased at the compound growth rate of about 0.1% from 2020 to 2030, elevating their market value to a stronger position. Gogoro was launched back in 2015 and with time, it has signed various pacts Yamaha, PGO, and various other companies.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Hero and Gogoro’s joint Venture</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The joint venture of Gogoro and Hero MotoCorp will instigate the designing of high-quality and maintained batteries for their automobile customers. These batteries will be based upon the world-known Gogoro technology, allowing the initiation of collaboration between a global brand and a local brand for the production of electric batteries, to be used in electric vehicles. Before this venture, many companies tried to invest in this project but there was not a single deal that worked out efficiently, and ultimately ended in failure. But this time it worked, as stated by the CEO of Gogoro Group- Horace Luke that they are getting ready to start the manufacturing process very soon. The only cause of the delay was that they have been waiting for the right time to enter into the market where their new techniques can be opened up for the investors, as well as all those companies who were reluctant in investing before to welcome investments, acting as a welcoming scheme for all the other interested companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Expansion of Deal</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The first part of this deal is to swap the battery production in both countries; where the production unit will be in charge of making batteries for Hero MotoCorp, which will then be used for the electric-based two-wheeler vehicles. Over time, this pact will see more growth, allowing Gogoro to join hands with 40 other countries, thus becoming a global chain. This will then open opportunities and pave way for the investors and all the local companies to become a part of this group. The projected cumulative growth rate of the company can increase up to 2 billion USD per year, which will help the company to expand its growth. This pact with the Hero group will give a rapid boost to their market as India has a bigger market standing than Taiwan, hence it can give multiple sections to the group to open up their swapping station and increase their rapid network.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Gogoro all set to enter Asian Market', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Economics,Hot Updates', '1623069962_mandy-zhu-_JtLAHMyVwM-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:46:02'),
(64, 'binance-to-launch-new-nft-marketplace', 'Tue, 04 May 2021 11:36:39 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Binance is considered one of the recognized cryptocurrency platforms around the world. Out of all other platforms, Binance has made its place in the market as one of the most authentic and trusted platforms, where all the new currencies are launched. Binance has a variety of cryptocurrency trends, along with their detailed information and ways that will help you in investing in your choice of cryptocurrency. Another amazing feature which this platform has is the updating schedule of all the new cryptocurrencies that are ready and set to be launched in the stock market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This application is all set and ready now to move one step further as they plan to launch their non-fungible tokens in the stock market. With the launch of these tokens, a new marketplace will be set that will allow the trading of these tokens along with the buying and selling of all cryptocurrencies. According to the various reports, it is also confirmed that Binance is all set and prepared to go live in the marketplace in June this year. The month decided for the launch is June because it will be half the fiscal years of all the banks and the economic condition will also get cleared by the half-yearly report.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>NFT Tokens favorable or unfavorable&nbsp;</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before the pandemic, NFT was considered a new hype in the market. These tokens were the new hype in the market and every other brand or business was rushing to avail this opportunity and maximize the usage of tokens. But as soon as the pandemic hit the world, their value decreased -0.3% in the total world market. It is reported that the current situation of NFT in the global market is deteriorating every passing day. When the spokesperson of Binance was questioned about the launching of NFT, he told that it is considered a “Strategic Move” and this move will promote NFT trading in the world as the platform gains a stable place in the global market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Furthermore, the additional enhancements that Binance will provide will include free trading of Ethereum NTS containing crypto punks and Hashmaks. These will be enabled on the platforms and will offer them a 10% discount. The cumulative fees that will be charged on this platform will be 10% of the total investment that you have performed, with 90% of it to be returned to the investors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Division of Platforms</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The main purpose of this platform is that it is to be used for buying &amp; selling, and for conducting premium events. The high-end premium events will be used for high-end exhibitors and high-end payments. This will not involve a single user but big names which are associated with big firms and businesses. The trading platform will accommodate all the users who are utilizing this platform for investment purposes, hence will be considered a game-changer in the global economy as many users will form trading grounds by investing and profiting the maximum amount of money from this platform.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Binance to launch new NFT Marketplace', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Crypto Apps,Crypto Mining News,Strategic Financial Management', '1623069951_executium-xYFNDku8eH0-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:45:51');
