(76, 'make-up-brands-ruling-over-the-stock-market', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 13:47:43 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During the post-pandemic time, a sudden change in the market has been observed as the stocks are changing their positions haphazardly. On a weekly basis, there is an upheaval in the market. If we look at the global stock market in the past week, there was a day when social media websites and e-commerce sites were ruling the stock market. Similarly, there were days when the stock charts and share market were ruled by cryptocurrency. But today, the market shocked the world through a surprisingly amazing move when a big makeup tycoon- Estee Lauder took over the top position in the charts and a new price record was set.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Record changing Statistics</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Estee Lauder took a lead in the stock market as their first quarterly market share was sold for 1.63cents per share. Although the revenue generation for this will be slow, however, the overall impact on the shares was massive and will continue to increase as the market trading remain unrelenting at 3.56% of the overall market trading. This is by far considered the best trading record by any of the makeup brands and has set up a new milestone as it is the first time in history for an international makeup brand in a global market to start producing the maximum amount of business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The second giant whose shares were ruling the market was Meredith Corp, another media conglomerate that started ruling when the profit was about 11.5% in the total market. It is also in the report that they are going to sell 17 of their stations to Gray Television network, the net worth of which encompasses nearly about $2.5 billion. No competition from any similar brand lines was seen in the market’s leading charts this week. Usually, the start of the week is considered as a single tone lead where the similar brands have a competition but this time there was a difference in the chart as a scattered distribution of the shares was observed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Which companies are in the competition?</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With this sudden change, numerous companies were seen competing in the market across the globe; From Dell to Moderna to Novartis, all the companies were fighting neck to neck to gain top ranks in the share price. The competition went real tight when the investors got into real trouble about where to invest. According to the market survey, the reports showed that the investors were reluctant to invest in Estee Lauder but they showed enthusiasm in financing in any other companies like Novartis, Dell, Moderna, and Tilray, resulting in an increase in the price of 1%, 3%, and 2.3%, respectively.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Estee Lauder is not static in its share price and can face a depression anytime in the market. To play safe, the investors invested in the safe hands so that the money can generate profit from 0.5% to 1%. Although this is a strategic move from the company, it can decrease the market share price of Estee Lauder in near future.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Make-up brands ruling over the Stock Market', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Stockwatch', '1623069288_antonin-fels-OdqmOsUgNwk-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:34:48'),
(77, 'apple-facing-issues-in-european-countries', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 13:49:26 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple is a globally recognized name in the technology industry. For a very long time, Apple has been leading the global markets and its shares were considered to be the finest shares were willing to invest within no time. With the demise of Steve Jobs, there was a decrease seen in the fame of the company along with a big plunge in their business statistics and global shares in the market. With the keen efforts of the company, the hard work turned fertile and paid off when the entire company pulled up its name again as the leading company. However, with fame, one has got to face its repercussions. Now Apple is entangled in another serious issue that can give them a huge break in their existing business. The company is facing serious trust issues with European countries and a crackdown is probably expected soon. Initially, they were able to pull out themselves from the market but now the issue is gaining pace with their dominance in the market using mean ways.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Google and now Apple</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A couple of years back, Google faced severe issues where it faced a major crackdown on the privacy policy and general data rules and regulations. This issue was faced by the European countries where the policies were not according to their terms and a heavy fine was imposed on Google that caused them a heavy setback in the stock market with a decrease of 3.6%. This was the time when investors held their hands back from investing in this business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Likewise, Apple is now facing another issue, which according to the antitrust policy in the European countries was observed when they used their abusive and dominant powers in the market to get the hold of the distributing powers. The company statement claimed that this illegal ban is imposed by the music application Spotify whereas some implications are imposed on the company by The App Store. These implications are not imposed by The Play Store but they have charged them on iTunes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>European Tax crackdown</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It has been observed by the analysts and review companies that this crackdown may lead to a major tax crackdown on Apple, causing a major blow of about 1.7% of loss in the market. This can be a reason for investors to back off from their total shares in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to a total estimate, about $14.5 billion is the net worth of the tax that will be paid by the company to get the ban off. This makes a total of 5.9% of the half-quarterly year share of the company produced. In a statement given by the company, Apple revealed that they will re-look into this matter and appeal in the European courts to seek some help before paying this heavy fine. Some researchers say that if the company is proved guilty, this will be a major blowout on their name and can affect their total market worth causing a major price reduction in various components in the future.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Apple facing issues in European Countries', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,News &amp; Updates,Stockwatch', '1623069273_bangyu-wang-omoCm0bvNW4-unsplash (1).jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:34:33'),
(78, 'the-gates-wealth-assets-and-philanthropy', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 13:52:49 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mixed news came from The Gates as Bill Gates ended the decade richer than before and one of the wealthiest couples decided to call it quits after 27 years of marriage, sharing three children. Their combined philanthropic move of a charity foundation built on their own name has shocked the world of philanthropy. The Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation declared its net assets worth 43.3 billion dollars in 2019 alone. Even though the couple has decided to part ways, they have established to keep working together at the foundation, for the foundation. Bill Gates stepped down as Microsoft board last year to focus more on his charity work and his role as a co-chair at one of the world’s largest charitable organizations. Their divorce is the second-high profile divorce after Amazon founder Jeff Bezo’s divorce from MacKenzie last year, ending their 25 years of marriage.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What happens to their assets now?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the absence of a prenuptial agreement, US law of community property states that the assets and wealth garnered during the course of marriage must be divided into equal halves between the spouses. If the husband owns more, he divided his assets. Similarly, if the wife owns more, she divides her assets. Of course, the divorce settlement can be negotiated between the two parties and it can be divided in a different ratio.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bill Gates is the world’s fourth-richest man on the planet right now. According to Forbes magazine, his net worth is a whopping 130.5 billion dollars. After finding Microsoft with his friend Paul Allen, Gates owned 49% of the share which catapulted him into fame and massive wealth, instantly making him a multi-millionaire back in 1986. Competitive companies in the market and his career in philanthropy made him lose his title of the richest man, ranking him to fourth place. Melinda and Bill’s love story started in 1987 when she joined Microsoft as a fresh graduate. Forbes regards Melinda Gates as the “most powerful woman” in the world of philanthropy. Their foundation was founded in 2000 with the aim to donate to causes of public health, education, infectious diseases, and climate change. Stats provided by the foundation’s website show that worth 1.75 billion dollars of grants was dedicated to vaccine initiatives, research, and diagnostics.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All assets are not disclosed to the public and the public has appealed to be given space and privacy during the process of divorce settlements. What we do know is that the couple’s main residence located at Lake Washington is estimated at 130.8 million dollars in 2020. It’s an understatement to call the seven-bedroom mansion a residence. Other joint property disclosed to the common public includes houses in the states of Florida and California, and a cherry on top is the private jet! Inheritances are usually not divided in the situation of a divorce, so the couple is seeking to divide their joint assets amicably according to the separation settlement they have reached the King County Superior Court.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Gates’ Wealth, Assets and Philanthropy', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currencies,News &amp; Updates', '1623069169_bram-van-oost-6WvZo5FOxww-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:32:49'),
(79, 'mexican-economy-shrinking-day-by-day', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 13:57:32 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mexico is considered one of the richest countries in the world. It was leading the world charts in the year 2017 and according to various reporters across the globe; it was considered that by the end of 2018 the country’s economy will be increased by 3.2% in total. By the end of the year 2018, the Mexican economy was in the top 20 economies and standing tall at the thirteenth number. However, by the end of the year 2019, when the world got hit by the global Covid-19 pandemic, all countries faced a major setback in their economies causing a drastic financial crisis. While all the countries are lagging in this particular aspect, the Mexican economy is depreciating every passing day.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Contracted Economy in 2021</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With time, the world is getting clenched into the claws of the pandemic more and more with its new strains coming out every few months. This is affecting all the dominant countries, causing major financial losses. The market is saturating day by day and the annual GDP of numerous countries has faced an overall decline. According to a recent survey conducted, the economy of Mexico is decreasing every passing month; it was expected that the economy might see a positive gain but from February, the economy has been facing a downfall. The record-breaking downfall was observed in 1932 by the economy of Mexico when it contracted by 5.1 %. A similar situation was faced by the country last year when the economy dropped by 5-5% due to the Corona pandemic. This was considered as a mega-global hit to any country and the total decline of 0.5% by each month.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Latin America’s declining economy</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to a series of surveys conducted, it is observed that during the second trimester of the pandemic, the overall economy of Latin America economy faced a decline of about 18.3% which was by far the highest plunge seen by any group of the countries. The biggest victim in this plunge was Mexico and the country has faced major debts. The government did little to support the businesses. According to President of Mexico- Lopez Obrador, the country is showing a positive sign in the economy. Contrary to that, the country was short of 8000 jobs because of which the youngsters had to face major life issues. The people of Mexico were also not happy with the governance system. It is observed from the global statistics that the Mexican Economy was already facing loss and the government did not support the growing businesses by supporting them. The inflation may increase because if all the resources are going to get utilized, the country will face major starvation. These all situations started to lead towards a major global issue where they face a global economic crisis. The only reason to get past this setback and recover from the loss incurred is to increase the primary elements like farming and fishing, and increase its import so that the crisis may be abridged.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mexican Economy Shrinking day by day', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,News &amp; Updates', '1623069142_christy-ash-6x8HIxH2eKI-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:32:22'),
(80, 'indian-billionaire-advises-to-curtail-economic-activity', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:00:20 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>India is on the front line, battling the deadly pandemic and the situation becomes grimmer than the previous day. India recorded over 3600 deaths in a day, making it the highest figure yet. With total cases pushed to 19.56 million, Indian industry body and billionaire, Uday Kotak, has advised Modi and the government to take maximum steps to contain virus transmission. The managing director of Kotak Mahindra Bank urged the authorities to put their foot down and take maximum precautionary measures which could be brutal to save Indian lives and livelihoods. The country’s health system is overwhelmed and the oxygen supply is depleted since the new variant is deadlier and has a higher transmission rate. Uday Kotak is an influential businessman of India; he is also the president of the Confederation of Indian Industry. Speaking at an event on Sunday, he expressed on the behalf of the confederation, “At this critical juncture when the toll of lives is rising, CII urges the strongest national steps including curtailing economic activity to reduce suffering.”&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>India under siege:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Covid-19 continues to grip India with tight, sharp claws. Prime Minister Narendra Modi is against imposing lockdowns to curb the spread of the virus since India saw its economic output fall by a staggering figure of 24 percent in the fiscal quarter April to June 2020, as compared to the same quarter of 2019. However, 11 states have imposed some form of lockdowns, including the northern state of Haryana and the eastern state of Odisha, both of which happen to be important industrial states of India. According to reports published in national newspapers on Sunday, Covid-19 task forces are urging the government to enforce a nationwide lockdown.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Modi seems to be adamant about not imposing lockdowns as he did last year. Stats provided by the Centre for Monitoring Indian Economy show the highest unemployment rate recorded in May 2020, 21.73 percent. The situation remained unstable throughout 2020, continuing into 2021. On average, the unemployment rate remained around 8 percent. The difference between March 2021 and April 2021 is quite striking. CMIE records it at 6.50 percent and 7.97 percent respectively. At a 30 day moving average, the unemployment rate is at 8.0 percent as of 2nd May 2021.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Falling economic output and crashing unemployment are preventing the ruling government from imposing a nationwide lockdown. Kotak sympathized with the health care workers at the same event on Sunday and said that they will not be able to handle the immense influx of covid-19 patients. The shortage of medical staff is adding to the trauma of the country. Although international aid is pouring in to accommodate them, the country is still running out of space in crematoriums and morgues. Visuals have gone viral on social media of dead bodies being burned on streets, families running out of wood, and bricks to cremate their loved ones. Ambulances are transporting as many as 22 dead bodies in one go.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The situation in India during the second wave is a tear-jerker, and steps need to be taken which could be brutal to the economy but kind to families and loved ones.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Indian Billionaire Advises To Curtail Economic Activity', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Currencies,Hot Updates', '1623069119_sergio-capuzzimati-R1CGt8exzLg-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:31:59'),
(81, 'robin-hood-all-set-to-make-record-amount-in-business', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:03:52 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Robin Hood is not a new name for marketers, businessmen, and investors in the stock market. It is a well-reputed organization that has established itself with its authentic trading and stock ventures. From small companies to big companies, all rely on Robin Hood for trading. The company launched their application in 2015, which has enabled various users to get the advantage. The hands-on feature of Robin Hood has been a motivational factor for various investors in the market.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The global stock market is showing major variations of trends for a couple of weeks. There are no stagnant shares that are leading. A few days back, Robin Hood started leading the market with the record-breaking price of $331 million through their stock trading application. This is considered as a record-breaking price attained by any company using e-platforms.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Early statistics of Robin Hood</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The market research conducted in the last few years tend to be accurate as in last year September 2020, the company’s net worth was $12 billion, which was later increased in February 2021 by giving more than 100% profit to the company and increasing its total net up to $40 billion. This is the record-breaking price ever maintained by any stock market/ company. This drastic increase was also recorded in the stock market where the company was able to get the record-breaking investment in a day and the buying and selling reached a record price giving a new market dip.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The total business achieved in the first quarter of the year 2021 is double to that of what they achieved in the first quarter of 2020, i.e. the record price was reached from $91 million in 2020 to $221 million in just the first half of 2021, which is a record in itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><strong>Robin Hood going life on NASDAQ</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Robin Hood has expanded very quickly in the market. Whether it is from an e- platform or application or live investment, it has shown a remarkable spread. Robin Hood will be going live soon on NASDAQ. This news itself was a big help to the company as the investors started to invest more because it will double their value in the profit shares. The breaking of this news gave a boom to the business from $133 million to $ 198 million. These investments have not only benefitted the investors but gave a remarkable place to the business in the global stock market where the company shares and the net worth of the company also increased.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The increasing trends have given the best repute to the company in the market. One of the great investors- Warren Buffet while talking about Robin Hood said that now it is useful for all the business owners and investors. It has particularly given a lot of benefits to the Casino owners and casino market as well; as people in casinos prefer investing towards share rather than money. This has also created uncertainty towards various investors because now people prefer a business with Robin Hood instead of doing business with the big investors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Robin Hood All Set to Make Record Amount In Business', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,News &amp; Updates,Strategic Financial Management', '1623069094_maxim-hopman-fiXLQXAhCfk-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:31:34'),
(82, '5th-time-s-the-charm-for-space-x-starship', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:05:42 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you find a formal definition for a Starship, multiple definitions come up. All of which define as existing only in science fiction. I quote a direct definition from Freebase,&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“A starship or interstellar spacecraft is </em><strong><em>a theoretical spacecraft</em></strong><em> designed for traveling between stars, as&nbsp;opposed&nbsp;to a vehicle designed for orbital spaceflight or interplanetary travel. The&nbsp;term&nbsp;is mostly found in science fiction, as humans have not yet constructed such vehicles.”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The reality is stranger than fiction and we have outdated dictionaries since starships are not theoretical anymore. Humans, rather Space X, have constructed a Starship that just underwent a successful test flight. After four failed attempts to launch and land a Starship prototype, an ever-optimistic Musk had the pressure of succeeding in the fifth attempt. It was absolutely imperative for the Starship prototype to make a successful landing this time because Space X was lucky in securing funding from NASA in the shape of a contract with a promise to complete their Artemis moon program which would transport astronauts to the moon by the mid-2020s. NASA’s contract worth 2.89 billion US dollars left a sour taste in Jeff Bezo’s and Alabama-based defense contractor. Both own Blue Origin and Dynetics respectively which are the main contenders for Musk’s Space X. Bezos commented that this contract will create a monopoly in private space exploration and transportation programs.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What does it mean for related companies?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Musk has been successful in launching and landing a reusable rocket which has the potential of saving as much as 30 million US dollars each time a rocket is launched. Instead of carrying a conventional crowd of 3-4 astronauts at a time, Starship has the capacity of transporting 100 people to as far as Mars. Take an example of launching a shuttle to LEO orbit: NASA Space shuttles cost $54,500/kg, while SpaceX’s Falcon 9 (2010) and Falcon Heavy (2018) cost $2,720/kg and $1,410/kg respectively.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Positive development in the stock market:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While you can’t directly buy shares of Space X since it’s privately held and under the umbrella of Tesla CEO Elon Musk, you can buy shares of private space start-ups who are going public with the help of SPACs. From a stock market perspective, it gives buyers and investors an opportunity to join in on a new adventure of space commercialization and entrepreneurship. After the mergers of start-ups with SPACs close, Barron lists around 13 billion US dollars’ worth of seven such stocks that will be open to the public. They include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/ASTS\">AST SpaceMobile</a>&nbsp;(Market Cap at $1.39 bn)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/SRAC\">Stable Road Acquisition</a> (Market Cap at $243.18 mn)</li><li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/articles/momentus-wins-a-moon-order-as-space-economy-heats-up-51606759263?mod=article_inline\">Momentus;&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/VACQ\">Vector Acquisition</a> (Market Cap at $410.8 mn)</li><li>Helicity (Market Cap at $384 mn)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/SFTW\">Osprey Technology Acquisition</a> (Market Cap at $392.55 mn)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/NSH\">NavSight</a>&nbsp;(Market Cap at $284.62 mn)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/quote/stock/GNPK\">Genesis Park Acquisition</a> (Market Cap at $205.54 mn)</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Although Space X has been marked private (for now), it is worth a whopping $74 billion in the private market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '5th Time’s The Charm for Space X Starship', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Hot Updates,News &amp; Updates', '1623068610_tyler-lastovich-7FDIUNvKkIU-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:23:30'),
(83, 'the-greenback-is-up-again-eurusd-being-hammered-down-by-the-bears', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:10:40 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The greenback is up again - EURUSD being hammered down by the bears!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dollar has finally decided to take back what it lost during the past 2 weeks. USD has been facing a lot of pressure from the bears, US economy and Covid-19. The greenback has been falling to the bottom since the beginning of 2021. Interestingly, not only the big fish have been wining against it, even its weakest rivals took advantage of its deteriorating position in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EUR, GBP, JPY, CNY, all have been winning against USD. INR and PKR, the weaker currencies, gained some ground against USD. Investors lost confidence and things were not going in favor of the greenback, at all!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, the tables have now turned in favor of USD and it seems to be making a rebound that would last long. The greenback is finally out of the bearish pressure and is ready to claim its bullish positions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A brief history and future outlook</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The demand for USD on Wednesday saw a sudden spike and EURUSD fell by a low but steady margin of 0.1%. Even though this margin wasn\'t significant enough to trigger a market reaction, the reality was quite the opposite. A fall in EURUSD caught the attention of investors and within moments, the demand for greenback was strong again. The shortage of supply pushed greenback higher and EUR had to move down in order to balance out the equation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A major reason behind this strong market reaction was USD\'s performance over the last 3 days. The greenback has been improving slightly, every single day. If you look at the accumulated figures, USD graph would show you an upwards trend that is about to continue for a medium term at least. Hence, another 0.1% improvement against a strong currency boosted the investor confidence and demand for USD increased as a result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently, the pair is revolving around $1.19 and is expected to go below $1.15 within the next 3 trading days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The chief US economist at High Frequency Economics explained this improvement in the following words:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dollar has finally decided to take back what it lost during the past 2 weeks. USD has been facing a lot of pressure from the bears, US economy and Covid-19. The greenback has been falling to the bottom since the beginning of 2021. Interestingly, not only the big fish have been wining against it, even its weakest rivals took advantage of its deteriorating position in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EUR, GBP, JPY, CNY, all have been winning against USD. INR and PKR, the weaker currencies, gained some ground against USD. Investors lost confidence and things were not going in favor of the greenback, at all!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, the tables have now turned in favor of USD and it seems to be making a rebound that would last long. The greenback is finally out of the bearish pressure and is ready to claim its bullish positions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A brief history and future outlook</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The demand for USD on Wednesday saw a sudden spike and EURUSD fell by a low but steady margin of 0.1%. Even though this margin wasn\'t significant enough to trigger a market reaction, the reality was quite the opposite. A fall in EURUSD caught attention of investors and within</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The greenback is up again - EURUSD being hammered down by the bears!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currency Market,News &amp; Updates', '1623068532_markus-spiske-ms6N-gBtbCQ-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:22:12'),
(84, 'dollar-moves-north-shares-fall-nasdaq-in-deep-trouble', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:14:48 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NASDAQ lost investor confidence on Tuesday morning and is now under a heavy bearish pressure. The share indexes have fallen worldwide and the US treasury is now in the pessimistic region once again. The economic outlook seems to be going southwards as well, putting investments at risk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The scenario has forced many investors to sell their shares, in fact, after the potential growth seemed to vanish away earlier today, investors began a selling streak which further damaged NASDAQ and pinned it down to the ground. Investors\' concerns are also quite valid, the current economic situation of the USA is not optimistic at all. US has been fighting against Covid19 for a long time now, even though some progress has been made, the pandemic has caused a lot more damage than what has been recovered yet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to these disappointing economic elements, US treasury stocks decline today hammered the final nail in the coffin. The current market scenario is expected to be in favor of the bears this week and the bulls can\'t do much about it. Having said that, USD has gained some ground today that will be discussed later in this article.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The fall of NASDAQ</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NASDAQ set a new low record on Tuesday. The index fell by a huge 2.7%, highest during the last 6 weeks. These stats were already pushing down the shares when the US treasury jumped in to make things even worse. The 10 year treasury yield fell to its lowest level at 1.557%, pushing away all risk averse investors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Soon, a selling trend was noticed in the market which spread globally like a wildfire in just a few moments. However, we noticed something interesting in this trend. Normally, when US treasury yield falls, the technology shares appreciate in value. This mechanism was rejected today and even with the yield facing a decline, the tech shares failed to make a rebound.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Palladium, on the other hand, managed to take advantage of the situation. The auto-catalyst\'s prices went high as the day moved on. A major reason behind this upwards spike was the difference between demand and supply. The recent charts show an increased demand for Palladium followed by an insufficient supply.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Furthermore, CRB edged higher and set a 3 year high record as investors made bets in favor of commodity demands. Even though the current economic conditions of the country are not very optimistic, investors believe that the economy is about to make a comeback soon and that is when the demand for commodities will rise. This positive outlook pushed up the CRB index and the market got even more complicated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A major part of decline in NASDAQ was played by Amazon, Apple inc and Microsoft. In fact, the ripple effect caused by this decline made a great impact on S&amp;P 500 as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"There\'s not a lot of conviction among traders of which way markets should go from here, we\'ve priced in a great amount of reopening optimism.\" -Patrick Leary, chief market strategist at Incapital.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nasdaq is currently under great deal of pressure, USD is improving slowly but the current financial situation seems to be an illusion with inaccurate signs. We\'ll know more about America\'s situation as the week moves on.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting articles, keep visiting our website. Don\'t forget to subscribe before leaving!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Dollar moves North, Shares fall - NASDAQ in deep trouble!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Hot Updates,Stockwatch,Strategic Financial Management', '1623068494_tech-daily-ztYmIQecyH4-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:21:34'),
(85, 'gold-to-test-1818-level-before-moving-north-again', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:18:08 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gold is ready to go on a long northern journey and the bulls are excited for it. The king of Metals has shown a sign of an upwards trend last week and the upcoming weeks are going to move away from the bearish caves.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, in the short term, bears are expected to fight hard and when a bear takes something into grip, its not an easy job to get it free again!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The future expected trend line is a \"V\" in case of Gold but its origins lie far behind when XAUUSD was trading around $1680. If we look at it from that point onwards, the chart is definitely making a \"W\" formation which is right now in favor of the bulls.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The coming week would be surprising for investors. The yellow metal may have to surrender before making a comeback and that is not what most of us have been expecting!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Will $1818 touchdown push Gold towards $1900 level next month?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many analysts have been looking at the current trends of gold and are predicting a strong bullish movement in May. However, the reality is not as it is being shown. Gold is set to rise high on the charts but the current region is quite risky for it. A push through the resistance levels could boost Gold prices while a support trap could lead to a deep depression, yet again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is interesting to note that the history of Gold has been very unstable. The yellow metal has gained hundreds of dollars in a day but it has also lost nearly $1000 in the past. Even if the current momentum is in favor of the bulls, it isn\'t by any means a surety of a bullish future trend.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before moving on, let\'s first have a look at some important resistance and support levels for next week:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Resistance: $1845, $1873, $1900</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Support levels: $1818, $1789, $1755</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now the current position of Gold is in favor of the bulls and it is expected that after breaking $1845 resistance level, Gold will move up towards the next resistance level that will form around $1873 mark. If XAUUSD managed to cross $1900 mark, the metal will then aim towards a new world record and that is when the bullish reign would actually begin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the other hand, if the bulls are not able to break resistance level at $1845, Gold would crash straight to $1818 which will be a difficult test for the bulls. If that support level is broken by the bears, the King would fall and is expected to crash towards the early 1700s levels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is important to note that the recent history of Gold tells us that Gold has been hanging in the 1600s which is a threat to the bullish existence itself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As of now, Gold is trading above 9 periods EMA and 21 periods EMA along with a W chart formation which is clearly in favor of the bulls. However, the above mentioned support and resistance levels will be key points in identifying the future movement of Gold.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ll have to wait and see. Till then, keep visiting our website for more interesting content. Don\'t forget to subscribe before leaving!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Gold to test $1818 level before moving North again!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Currency Market,Gold,News &amp; Updates', '1623068448_sharon-mccutcheon-4jLj-GdRn_A-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:20:48'),
(86, 'dow-futures-appreciate-by-95-point-payrolls-are-set-to-rise', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:20:50 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>US stock market is finally making a comeback. The beginning of the week was not in favor of the US economy and we saw how NASDAQ fell, mainly because of the technology bubble pop.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interestingly, the revelation of April\'s job reports turned things around. US stocks that were under a bearish influence, now seem to be under complete control of the bulls. The latest DOW Jones industry average is a walking evidence and investors are have now gained back their lost confidence in the US economy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>USA has been affected adversely after the 1st and 2nd waves of covid pandemic. The initial trends of high unemployment and deteriorating economy are now vanishing with time. The greenback has faced some serious hammering during the last 3 weeks but it has managed to fight back and maintain an average position in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now as we move towards the end of this week, US stocks are showing signs of improvement. Here\'s what you need to know about it:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Are US stocks the next big thing in international market?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Earlier today, at 7:05 AM ET, the tables turned in favor of the US stock market. DOW Jones futures went up 95 points which wasn\'t a surprise at all. S&amp;P 500 futures traded at 10 points and NASDAQ, which has had a rough journey last week went up 32 points all of a sudden.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mathematically speaking, DOW Jones improved by 0.2%, S&amp;P 500 improved by 0.3% and NASDAQ 100 improved by 0.2%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This movement was expected by analysts who had been drawing an upward graph for US stocks since the last 4 days. In fact, the 4 day win streak reached its peak on Thursday during the American session after which DOW Jones closed 0.9% higher, S&amp;P 500 appreciated 0.8% and NASDAQ improved by a small, yet important margin of 0.4%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now the all trends are in favor of the US stocks and next week would be the game changer. The stocks are expected to grow rapidly during the next 5 trading days and USA might set a new high record!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The strong push on Thursday came after the employment report was revealed which now brings everyone\'s attention at the labor report.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How will the results of labor report make an impact on the US stocks and the US economy? Are we moving towards a longterm bullish trend? Or the stocks have to retreat?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, its too early to predict right now. The stocks are on a rise!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The ET stock rose 5.2% today after the company announced a 2.4 Billion gain from Texas Winter Storm. PTON gained 6.7% after the company revealed a 135% increase in quarterly subscriptions. However, some stocks like SHAK and BYND caught attention for the negative reasons. These stocks saw a decline, 8% and 7% respectively due to disappointing financial results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The overall trends are in favor of the US economy as of now. The stock market is expected to appreciate next week and investors are ready to buy it all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more helpful analysis, keep visiting our website. Help us grow by sharing this article with your friends and family!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'DOW Futures appreciate by 95 point - Payrolls are set to rise!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Stockwatch', '1623068352_annie-spratt-hWJsOnaWTqs-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:19:12'),
(87, 'gbpusd-in-reach-of-the-bears-again', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:25:07 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The month of April has been bearish for GBPUSD but May proved to be in favor of the bulls. GBPUSD has been trying to maintain a consistent level but the immense pressure from both sides has made it inconsistent, unreliable and volatile.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GBPUSD is once again near the bearish region and bulls are expected another bearish takeover soon. An accurate predicted outlook would be helpful at this point in time but the current situation wouldn\'t allow it to happen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So what exactly is going to happen next week? Are we looking at a sharp bearish turn or the pair would simply continue its journey towards North?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let\'s find out.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>GBPUSD\'s Bearish April Journey</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GBPUSD had a rough month but it defended itself well. The month of April was clearly a victory for the bears. The pair fell down to its lowest level, at $1.37 on 30th April 2021, ringing alarm for the bulls.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Interestingly, from there on, the mechanism worked in favor of the bulls. You see, forex is a complicated financial market which could reveal the most unexpected trends at any time of the year. That is exactly what happened to GBPUSD. After crashing down to $1.37 by the end of April, instead of breaking the support level, it turned into a resistance level which was broken by the bulls!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The pair has, since then, moved upwards and is currently aiming towards the opposite of what we saw last month.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>GBPUSD expected to fall back in May</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The current scenario, however, is once again in favor of the bears. Surprisingly, GBPUSD has been under a complete bullish control since the beginning of May 2021. In fact, the pair has already touched $1.40 and is aiming towards $1.45 level. But that won\'t be as simple as it seems to be.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GBPUSD is facing a strong resistance at $1.40 and this resistance will actually decide the future of this pair. If bulls are able to break out of this resistance level, the pair will experience a strong upward trend. If the bulls fail to break this resistance level, the pair will crash down to previous month\'s support, that is, $1.37 level.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If that happens, GBPUSD would crash down to $1.35 in a matter of days!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Important levels to notice</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some important levels to notice during the upcoming weeks before investing any amount in this pair:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. For bulls: 1.40, 1.4150, 1.43</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. For bears: 1.39, 1.38, 1.3650</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here we have mentioned two series, one for the bulls, one for the bears. The reason behind this is that if bulls successfully break the current resistance levels, the pair would gain momentum in favor of the bulls but it would go towards the overbought region.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now the pair is trading above 2 EMA, and the 9 period EMA is still hanging above the 21 period EMA which clearly point towards a bullish trend. Once the pair gains this bullish momentum, a corrective action would come into play, reseting the pair back towards the lower levels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That is where the bears will jump in and take control of it in order to set a new low record in their favor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting articles, keep visiting our website. Don\'t forget to subscribe before leaving!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'GBPUSD in reach of the Bears again!', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Currency Market,Economics,News &amp; Updates', '1623068321_colin-watts-8WRRJ4xJeyg-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:18:41');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `post_url`, `pubDate`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `post_author`, `post_category`, `post_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(88, 'dollar-jumps-up-again-after-revelation-of-central-bank-s-latest-policy', 'Mon, 10 May 2021 14:42:41 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The month of May has proven to be favorable for the greenback. US dollar is finally back in the game and is now ready to launch towards the higher side of the market. As trading began on Monday, USD experienced a sudden spike, thanks to the new Central bank policy that helped boost the investor confidence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, this upward movement might change direction during the next half of the week. The US economic data us yet to be revealed which will draw a clear picture of where USA currently stands in terms of global inflation and the responses made by the policymakers to minimize the damage caused by Covid19.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Moreover, Central Bank has yet to reveal certain decisions that would make an impact on the Financial part of the economy. The current bullish trend is seen as an illusion by some experts while many are considering it as the beginning of a bullish journey. Let\'s have a look at the current standings of USD against its rivals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>US dollar vs Competitors</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>DXY is in process of stabilization. The greenback\'s index just recovered by a tiny margin of 0.07% on Monday, setting up its new position at 91.330 level as the day ended. The USD index contains a bundle of rival currencies and an increase in value signaled towards a bullish USD ride. The following are the current standings of USD against competitors:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. The USDJPY pair appreciated by a moderate 0.29% level, boosting investor confidence in other parts of the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. The AUDUSD pair was up by a tiny margin of 0.05% but this didn\'t make an impact on the USD confidence levels. The reason behind this upward movement was the revelation of Australian Industry Group Manufacturing index which claimed 61.7 level of April compared to previous month\'s 59.9 reading. This helped AUD move up and as a result USD faced minor losses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. As a result, NZDUSD pair also inched up towards the 0.7176 level or 0.22% but again, these changes triggered no market reaction as far as USD was concerned.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. USDCNY pair remained consistent at 6.47 level which again shows a better performance of USD which had been declining against CNY in the past.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5. And finally, the GBPUSD pair was under a minor bullish influence throughout the day, ringing alarms for the USD investors. The pair ended up 0.05% around 1.3821 level.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The only point of concern for USD today was the upwards movement for GBPUSD. All other rival currencies were in control of the greenback, in fact, the greenback was able to defeat many weaker currencies that have been trying to make a rebound against it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Another reason behind a stronger USD movement today was the Holiday declared in the Asian markets on Monday. China and Japan, two prominent markets were closed today and hence, USD took advantage of the situation to gain value against them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The current upwards trend of USD is expected to break down later this week. Investors have gained confidence in the greenback but many are still not willing to risk their investments in favor of it. Our analysis predicts a short term bullish movement for USD followed by a long term bearish trap.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more interesting articles, keep visiting us. Don\'t forget to subscribe before leaving!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Dollar jumps up again after revelation of Central Bank\'s latest policy', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Economics', '1623068285_bermix-studio-Xmgxjy-TzU0-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:18:05'),
(89, 'made-in-china-not-available-in-india-report', 'Tue, 18 May 2021 20:53:51 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>In a new move, India has withheld imports of ‘Made in China’ smartphones, Bluetooth speakers, wireless headsets and others: Report from Reuters</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>India is giving multinational tech companies a run for their money since it withheld the import of Chinese devices and parts from last November. Companies like USA’s Hewlett Packard (HP) and Dell and China’s Lenovo, Oppo, Xiaomi, and Vivo have been forced to delay their product launches in a massive profit-oriented market. Two industry sources have revealed to Reuters news agency that India’s decision to suspend imports of parts made in China has impacted business in a key growth market – India. According to sources, parts manufactured in China include wifi modules, Bluetooth speakers, wireless headphones, smartwatches, smartphones, laptops, and other finished electronic products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lobbying efforts continue by tech firms to change the minds of Indian authorities sitting in India’s Communications Ministry’s Wireless Planning and Coordination (WPC) Wing, the ones who passed the order of withholding imports of finished electronic products from China. One of the sources reveals that these lobbying efforts are being made through the US, Korean, Chinese and, even Indian companies seeking clearance as soon as possible so any further delay of product launches may be avoided.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Is India blackmailing its way to economic growth?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>China is the world’s largest manufacturer when it comes to electronic items and parts. India is following suit fast. It has already become the world’s second-largest maker of mobile equipment. India’s ruthless policy against China comes under the orders of incumbent Prime Minister, Narendra Modi who is pushing for a more self-reliant and export-based economy. Clearly, his nationalist policy is bearing fruit as India’s smartphone assembly line has seen a boost and it has become the market’s second-largest producer of smartphone equipment. In Modi’s ideal economy of India, it produces its own electronic devices and urges companies using Chinese parts to replace them with Indian parts if they wish to sell their finished electronic goods in a key market, money printing market. One of the sources said, “The government’s idea is to push companies to manufacture these products in India”. Is this Modi’s way of blackmailing his way to an economic boost during the pandemic? We’ll just have to wait and see.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tech companies now find themselves in a difficult situation. If they decide to go for “Made in India” products, the waiting time is longer and this could result in a potential loss in revenues. Previously, India had a change of heart and allowed companies to self-declare their equipment. However, that change didn’t last long when India mandated new rules in March 2019, asking companies to seek government approval. Although India has earned the badge of the second-largest mobile maker, it still doesn’t have the resources, expertise, scale, workforce, or size to lure international companies into investing in “Made in India” or “Assembles in India”. Modi is demanding futuristic clearances in the present hurdles.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Made In China, Not Available in India: Report', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Don\'t Miss,News &amp; Updates', '1623068247_alana-harris-LH_Q8DBkgZ0-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:17:27'),
(90, 'google-jumping-high-in-the-remittance-market', 'Tue, 18 May 2021 21:02:12 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google has made a strong position in the market with its various products. From search engines to telephones, to its virtual assistants; Google is sparking everywhere. Google has emerged as a Big Business Giant in the market, and it is going to be a Big Conglomerate in the information technology industry. The latest trends in the stock market have pushed the investors as well to start investing in Google; the changing trends predict like the IT market, Google is going to lead the charts in global stocks and the global market. The increasing features and trends in the company are changing the market statistics of the company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>New Feature is up</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The new feature of Google is already up on the internet. For the European countries, it will not be a new feature. This feature is surely a new one for Asian Countries. Google Pay is all set to commence its work in India and Singapore. This feature is currently available in the US for Indian and Singaporean clients residing in their countries. According to the marketers, this is going to be a big strategic move that will help the countries to increase their global trading funds. The initial partnership of google pay is between Western Union and Wise through which the funds can be transferred easily between the countries. By far this is the biggest jump by any IT company in the remittance field but there is no plan for the company to become a global-local bank for the countries. This is just a feature for the transference of money.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Partnerships and Profit Generation</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google has pushed itself into the remittance field and started partnerships.&nbsp; The first thing is the launching of their own credit cards and financial billing schemes. This partnership is with Goldman Sachs in 2019. This was the time when the new version of this application was also launched in New York. These services will push themselves into the big remittance markets. The current partnerships of Google are with Facebook and Alibaba. The market survey states that World Bank is quite hopeful that remittances in the low and middle-income budget companies will have more profit generation. The worth can increase by $509 Billion in the year 2020. There can be a decrement that can be observed due to the current situation of the pandemic. This current feature is a big win for the WISE Company. It will be a big move in the market that will give a financial boost to the companies to generate more business.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This sudden change in the IT field will be a game-changer for many companies. This will open doors for the investors as well and this change in the market will start new trends. As per the spokesperson of Google, they are planning to expand this feature into more than 200 nations. This will cover more than 80 countries in the world where Western Union is covering and Wise as well. &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Google jumping high in the Remittance Market', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,Economics,News &amp; Updates', '1623068203_rajeshwar-bachu-K4txLik7pnY-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:16:43'),
(91, 'nio-ready-to-deliver-in-norway', 'Wed, 19 May 2021 05:53:13 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nio is not a new name in the automobile industry and is considered as the Chinese Tesla that has taken over the world with its unique design and spell bounding features. Chinese believe that Nio is going to take over the automobile industry shortly. These fancy features are considered to be the next century features as they are going to be totally automatic. This car is considered as the new luxury car where people are ready to invest.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to the market survey conducted by car enthusiasts, the upcoming models are going to beat Mercedes and Rolls Royce. The new features of Nio are bringing an exotic revolution in the automobile industry with cruise control, sonic speed, and budget-friendly investment.&nbsp; Initially, a Gallup survey gave deceiving comments about Nio, but the company emerged as a strong business tycoon in the automobile world. The net worth of the company is about US$7,081,505,000 (2020) which is a good outcome for the Chinese tech automobile company.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Nio Vs Tesla</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nio has shown fantastic growth in the first half-year quarter of 2021. The revenue generated by the company is the record generation throughout the years. In the month of January 2021, it was objected that the growth of the company has seen the shoot in revenue generation the amount was from $29.37% to $56.27%. By far this was the maximum amount which was seen in the growth of the company. These stats were really good to compete with Tesla as a beginner-level automobile company. These statistics were considered to be the game-changer in the market as the market cap of both companies was less than 19.7%. The market analysts revealed that this market cap can be covered within no time but somehow Tesla managed to bring up their shares to an increased level which again increased the market cap of the companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Nio launching in Norway</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to various reports, there was a rumor that Nio is all set to go global. The reports got the confirmation when the company issued the statement that the company is all set to launch their latest EV and MV in Norway and they are going global. This news was a major breakthrough in the stock market where a sudden boom was seen. This decision pushed the investors to come forward and invest in the company shares. The increase in the price of shares helped the company to reduce the market cap with Tesla which is their toughest competitor. The company spokesperson revealed that Nio is set to launch their latest models ES8 SUV and ET7 Sedan in 2022, but they will be first delivered in Norway.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This venture with Norway will be settled in Oslo at first and the next series of four to five showrooms will open in the upcoming year. This venture will give new recognition to the company and will help in expansion. Norway is considered the hub of electronic vehicles. Various companies like Nissan, Mazda, and Tesla have reached now Nio is ready to go. The other Chinese companies are also gearing up to head for Norway.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nio ready to deliver in Norway', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,News &amp; Updates', '1623068155_ernest-ojeh-UrCV-U9hhCo-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:15:55'),
(92, 'the-aftermath-of-ransomware-on-colonial-pipeline-europe-s-response', 'Wed, 19 May 2021 06:28:57 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Remember Game of Thrones? HBO was hacked and your favorite show’s several scripts were stolen and held ransom. In order to keep the suspense alive for you, HBO paid 250,000 dollars. Do you use Uber? Well, in 2016, they also paid 100,000 dollars to hackers who stole the data of 57 million drivers and passengers. Cyber espionage and ransomware have proven to be chaotic since the advent of internet and the digitization of sensitive files and private records. Recently, Alabama’s Colonial Pipeline was hit by a cyberattack committed by a group called Dark Side who not only demanded an insane amount of ransom money but also stole 100 gigabytes of data from Colonial’s network in just two hours. Can you imagine downloading a whole season of Game of Thrones worth 20 gigabytes in just two hours? This can bring some perspective to how powerful hackers are. Hackers are routinely holding sensitive records hostage and demanding millions in ransom in exchange for their release.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Secretary of Commerce Gina Raimondo said, “Unfortunately, these sorts of attacks are becoming more frequent. They\'re here to stay and we have to work in partnership with businesses to secure-secure networks, to defend ourselves against these attacks”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The United States is still trying to recover from the closure of main pipelines 1, 2, 3, and 4, while some lateral and small lines have been recovered and functioning. This attack has shed light upon the gruesome reality that there is an absence of plans to detect, decipher, deter, respond, manage and recover from a cyberattack on a national level. Reuters reports this incident as the most disruptive ransomware ever reported. It has prompted calls from US legislators to look into developing a better cybersecurity policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>European Commission’s response while the US stays silent:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The latest cyber attack has alerted a strong response from international communities which are now looking into ways to strengthen their firewall to hackers and ransom seekers at bay. The European Commission has planned to make 11 million euros available to fortify European Union’s competence to fight and deter any sort of cyber attacks, to invest into buying the latest technology and technicians to secure 22 new projects that are very sensitive and set to be launched in the following years. The projects are chosen under the Connecting Europe Facility program, through a recent call for proposals that support various projects in all of 18 member states. As defined by the European Union Cyber Security Act, the projects benefiting from this massive funding include Computer Security Incident Response (CSIR) teams, operators of essential services in the health, energy, transport, and other sectors, as well as bodies dealing with <a href=\"https://digital-strategy.ec.europa.eu/en/policies/cybersecurity-certification-framework\">cybersecurity certification</a> and testing. Between the years 2016 to 2020, European Commission has spent 47.5 million euros to fund and strengthen cyber security under the Connecting Europe Facility program. Moreover, a whopping 1 billion euros is set for the Digital Europe Program directed to focus on some areas of the EU Cyber Security Strategy. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The aftermath of Ransomware on Colonial Pipeline; Europe’s Response', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'News &amp; Updates', '1623068116_michael-geiger-JJPqavJBy_k-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:15:16'),
(93, 'more-italian-banks-expected-to-merge', 'Wed, 19 May 2021 06:31:43 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The banking sector in every country has pivotal importance in the growth of a country. The country’s significant growth depends upon the banking sector as they are the prime source for bringing up the business. The more business is brought into the bank the more revenue is going to be generated by the bank. The banking sector provides loans as well as they welcome the investors as well; the more the investors, there is a bright chance of the development of the country through the banking sector. Another trait of the banking sector is the trust of the local man of the country in them, a safe place they can invest with the hope that the revenue generated through the investment.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Italy has one of the most trusted banking sectors in the world. Their currency and Italian are recognized globally for their huge investments. A great number of Italian businessmen have emerged on the global list of rich people, who became successful due to their investments. The news was in the market that Italian banks are again going to merge. Before this, a few of the banking sectors were merged into one bank last year. This was a success for the Italian banking Industry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Intensa Sanpaolo’s Prediction</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In London, the spokesperson to Intensa Sanpaolo gave a bright hint of capitalization in the country. There was a clear sign that few small banks will be merged into the main big bank as the big bank will establish a stronger place in the market. According to the marketers, Europe is going to be the busiest marketplace in the year 2021 and the upcoming years. Various surveys were conducted in the market which reportedly said that small banks are looking for digitalization which will help the investors to get themselves a better place in the business sector. This digitalization also develops a strong pressure on smaller banks to get the merger.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Banco BPM and BPER Banca</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The reports of the merger started revolving in the market in the last half of 2020 but now it will take place in the first half of 2021. The reports also stated that Banco BPM and BPER Banca will go for a merger in Intesa Sanpaolo. This deal will give a huge benefit to both the banks as the amount of generated business through the merger will benefit these banks as well. The market also stated that more lenders in the market will give importance to small businesses. Italy is considered as one of the strict leaders by definition and virtue in the market and known as one of the risk-taking countries which have helped the country to establish themselves and their small businesses. Similar steps are going to be taken again by the biggest merger which will help the smaller banks to elevate their market status. This increment will lead to an increment in market shares, as well as the banking shares on Intesa Sanpaolo, resulting in an increase in the country’s economy and statistics on the global market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'More Italian Banks expected to merge', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Hot Updates', '1623068085_etienne-martin-2_K82gx9Uk8-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:14:45'),
(94, 'some-important-highlights-for-wednesday-stock-play', 'Wed, 19 May 2021 18:36:21 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>New Delhi:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As noted, Bulls held the post for the second consecutive day as the&nbsp;Nifty&nbsp;managed to close over the pivotal 15,100 level, enlisting the most noteworthy day by day close over the most recent 43 days. Purchasing interest in financials, auto and metals counters supported estimation as financial backers got more wealthy by Rs 2.8 lac crore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The index figured out how to frame a tiny bullish light on the every day chart, raising any expectations of additional potential gain. As per analysts, Nifty may observe further jump towards 15,200 and 15,350 levels in the event that it figures out how to hold the 15,100 level.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here\'s the way by which analysts assess the market trend:-&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mazhar Mohammad of Chartviewindia thinks Nifty requires to stay above the&nbsp;bullish void area&nbsp;present in the 15,043-14,938 zone. He said: “If this gap zone successfully offers support on dips, in course of time, the bulls can head higher to test their lifetime highs present around the 15,431 level. However, if the bulls fail to defend the 14,938 level on a closing basis, it can encourage the bears. Traders are advised to buy the weakness close to 15,000 level with a stop loss below 14,938 level on a closing basis.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was said by Gaurav Ratnaparkhi of Sharekhan that the list has crossed the 61.8 percent retracement of February-April fall and hopes to test the unsurpassed high of 15,431. Be that as it may, the assembly towards the high is probably not going to be an uneven excursion. There can be irregular interruption on the way up. The following obstacle is seen at 15,160 level, which is close the 78.6 percent retracement of February-April fall. The index can observe&nbsp; a short consolidation close to this key&nbsp;Fibonacci level&nbsp;before expanding higher. On the other side, any minor degree plunge is probably going to discover support close to the 15,000-14,940 zone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having that said, let us shed some light on some key indicators that are likely to be indicating the action for Monday</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The shares of US fall just when the telecom stocks drop down. S&amp;P 500 and the Dow also dropped on Tuesday, all this when sharp falls in telecom stocks. Alongside, a poor housing initiates data overshadowed upward earnings from Home Depot and the Waltmart. Moving forward around 9:10 pm IST, there was an average fall of Dow Jones at 83.75 points or in other words a percentage of 12 to 4158.30. The Nasdaq composite ended up gaining 49.22 points which makes in 0.37%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EU shares close to record highs</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>European stocks are seen closing record upward trends on Tuesday on optimism somewhat around several countries loosening up economic restrictions, dropping unemployment rate in the United Kingdom and powerful earnings report data from companies. At 9:10 p.m IST, the pan-European STOXX 600 index was at a rise of 0.26%, trading at a high record which it touched last week, with economy-related cyclical sectors such as oil, gas and miners, automakers heading with the gains. Last but not the least, the action of &nbsp; German DAX added on a 0.05% and Italy\'s FTSE MIB included 0.07%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Some Important Highlights for Wednesday Stock Play', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,News &amp; Updates,Stockwatch', '1623068041_chris-liverani-dBI_My696Rk-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:14:01'),
(95, 'goldman-sachs-losing-major-executives-slowly', 'Tue, 25 May 2021 09:15:04 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Goldman Sachs is not a new name in the banking investment industry. They have established their name in this field; a name that anyone can trust because of their outstanding features that have helped various parties on the individual and mega level that has allowed them to maintain the good position at which they are at today. They owe a big credit to Goldman Sachs for helping them out in times of need. When nobody came forward, Goldman Sachs appeared like a guardian angel for them out of nowhere and took them to golden heights.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For a couple of years, the repute of Goldman Sachs has been deteriorating because of the variety of competitors that have entered the investment banking sector. One of the big names that emerged and started giving tough competition to Goldman Sachs was JP Morgan Chase. Within no time, the repute of this company starting giving strong competition to the other renowned banking giants, not only in terms of market shares and stocks, but the companies are taking this competition to another level where they are taking away their thinking heads and leading executive officers. More perks, benefits, and other luxuries are working as a big bribe machine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>JP Morgan chase new the CFO</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few days back, the news was circulating around the media that JP Morgan Chase is looking for a new CFO and the hunting has already begun. But nobody was ready to witness a major upheaval in the banking sector when the newly appointed CFO was the ex- CFO of Goldman Sachs. The company was lucky enough to appoint Sherry Ann Mohan as the new CFO of JP Morgan Chase. By far, this is considered as the smartest move by any rival company by taking away their main head. This move has created many uncertainties in the small and big companies as this is an alarming situation. This situation was about to happen sooner or later due to internal conflicts of Goldman Sachs authorities. The executives were not happy with the decisions of signing MOU’s with some startups which lead to internal chaos and conflicts. The advantage was taken by the rivals at the right time where the higher executives were offered other perks by the rivals and they swiftly showed a transition from switching their companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Changes in the System</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not only the CFO but many other executives were also lured by the rivals to step down their position in the working company and they will be appointed on a good position in the other company. One of them was Sonali Divilek who was the head at Marcus, a sub-company of Goldman Sachs, but she refused the position as a new promotion was on her way when some other executives left the company. These changes in the company have shown a big impact on the stocks and shares of both of the companies. Goldman Sachs has seen a major decrease of 5% in the total of market shares whereas JP organ Chase has become a new sensation in the marketing sector with an increment of 9% of the share and stock prices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Goldman Sachs Losing Major Executives slowly', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Don\'t Miss,News &amp; Updates,Stockwatch', '1623068007_jordan-merrick-lMhkCwidlRY-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:13:27'),
(96, 'japan-s-economy-on-the-brink-of-a-double-dip-recession-fear-analysts', 'Tue, 25 May 2021 09:21:59 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japan is going through a tough year already, with five months in. Japan’s economy has shriveled far more than expected in the first quarter of 2021, fearing a double-dip recession. New variants of covid infections and a slow vaccine roll-out resulting in more lockdowns are the main factors of this shrunken economy. Latest government data revealed that the economy withered&nbsp;an annualized 5.1 percent in the first quarter, more than the forecast 4.6 percent contraction and following an 11.6 percent jump in the previous quarter, last year and domestic demand hit 1.1 percent point off gross domestic product (GDP), while net exports lessened by 0.2 points.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>World’s third-largest economy under pressure:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>More lockdowns were imposed in Japan as rules and police made sure residents stayed indoors to curb the rate of spread of infection which resulted in a 1.4 percent drop in private consumption. This covers dining out and retail shopping which dropped to an all-year minimum. The world’s third-largest economy’s export growth and capital expenditure also shrank unexpectedly as Japan struggles to bring it back on track. Businesses and companies cut back on spending on equipment for machinery and cars.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some analysts are of the opinion that strict, untimely lockdowns and a sharp decline in retail and capital expenditure may throw Japan into another recession, making it the second recession in a row in two fiscal quarters. Remember the global chip shortage? It has affected most exports of Japan. Chief market economist, Yoshimasa Maruyama explains, “Global chip shortages caused a marked slowdown in exports, putting a drag on capital spending as well… consumption will probably remain stagnant, raising risks of an economic contraction in the current quarter.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prime Minister Yoshihide Suga’s&nbsp;government is struggling to contain coronavirus cases while trying to speed up vaccine roll-out as well. Major economic areas, like malls, retail centers, and restaurants have been put under strict lockdown measures which are resulting in taking a big hit on Japan’s economy which was never fully recovered from the last fiscal quarter in the first place. To make matters worse, his administration added three more zones to the latest state of lockdown measures which put more than half of Japan’s economy at risk of not improving any time soon. If restaurants and bars are allowed to remain open, they are not allowed to sell alcohol and must close before sundown.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Japan is set to host the staging of the Tokyo Olympics and if these restrictions are not eased by the end of May, Japan would have to announce the bad news of its cancellation which would, you guessed it, be another blow to Japan’s economy. By early autumn, elections are also expected.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Economy Minister is also shuffling to make things right with Japan’s economy. If the vaccine roll-out does not pick up the pace, and strict lock down measures are not eased, the next fiscal quarter is expected to be even worse since Japan’s economy will not have a chance to recover at all. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Japan’s Economy on the Brink of a Double Dip Recession, Fear Analysts', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Economics,Hot Updates', '1623067811_nicki-eliza-schinow-BjJP2TN8WoI-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:10:11'),
(97, 'overseas-investors-are-ready-to-bring-money-to-china', 'Tue, 25 May 2021 09:27:39 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Despite the border conflicts of china with its neighboring country, the impact of clashes is observed in the stock market as well. The prices of various shares which are multinational based in China are facing it due to upheaval in the stock market. The Chinese market has observed major saturation in the last two years. Primarily, there are two main reasons for the major drop in the market. First is due to the Covid situation that got initiated from China itself and gave a major shock to the market. The second reason being the clashes at the Chinese border due to which instability is observed in the market but still many of the investors are looking forward to investing in China.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The difference that occurred in the monetary policies at the post-corona regain of money has started to increase which has opened up gateways for the overseas investors to bring in more money to China. The overall population of China has also started to increase, which was a good sign for the investors as well because it plays a significant role in bringing business back to the country.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Bonds and Investment in China</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Chinese JP Morgan bank and the bankers launched a new program on a hit and trial basis to see the response of the world which was a complete success for the Chinese banks. It started from the local investors which became a reason to boost the economic condition and bring stability to the country. Not only this, but these bonds got the attention of foreign investors as well who willingly commenced to invest dollars into this new program. The stability can be observed from the market statistics that it was launched in the last year and till date, the amount of funds which is gathered is almost $124 million under the client assets which shows the market has shown a rapid increase of about 8.7 % in the market. According to the experts the market has not changed, the only thing that has changed is the interest rate in the market which is rapidly increasing due to the increasing trend in the bond market. The market experts further revealed that in the coming three to five years this will increase up to 15% of the total rate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Chinese bond market</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to the recent survey conducted in the market, the Chinese bond market has topped the US bond market. The US market was at 3.22% whereas now the Chinese market has reached the top of 3.44%, setting a new record. By far, there has not been any other market of any Asian country to reach the world’s top country height. The Chinese market has sold bonds worth more than about 9million Yuan.&nbsp; Foreigners believe that by the end of this year, the interest rate of the lowest bonds will also increase from 4.89% up to 4.93%.&nbsp; This trend in the market has changed the world economic scenario where Chinese bonds are leading the market and in coming years globally these bonds will be accepted and considered as a benchmark of the world and market economy.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Overseas Investors are ready to bring Money to China', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Don\'t Miss,News &amp; Updates', '1623067777_kayla-kozlowski-ECQ-3QXThAA-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:09:37'),
(98, 'one-tweet-sends-bitcoin-crashing-to-an-all-time-low-in-three-months', 'Tue, 25 May 2021 09:33:03 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Elon Musk, the tech and space giant, made bitcoin legitimate by investing 1.5 billion dollars. Bitcoin went soaring to its highest with an increasing number of investors pouring in money to buy more and more bitcoins. This was just in February. Virtual currency was on the verge of becoming a mainstream asset when the same Elon Musk brought it down to an all-time low in just a period of three months. He has a following of 55.6 million users on Twitter alone, so one can imagine the magnitude of consequence when he tweeted the following on Monday,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“Do you want Tesla to accept Doge?”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He tweeted this in the form of a poll, asking his half a billion followers. 78.2 percent of them voted with a ‘yes’. Many believe that this tweet is suggestive in the sense that either Tesla has sold its bitcoins or is about to sell them. Either way, investors started pulling money out of the bitcoin investment after fears of illegitimacy attached to bitcoins. However, it’s good news for doge coins. This single tweet sent bitcoin to its lowest, that is, more than 9 percent which makes it 42,185 dollars. Lingering skepticism surrounding virtual currency came back with full force, it seems.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>@CryptoWhale, an unverified Twitter account, tweeted,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“Bitcoiners are going to slap themselves next quarter when they find out Tesla dumped the rest of their #Bitcoin holdings. With the amount of hate @elonmusk is getting, I wouldn’t blame him…,”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Musk responded to this tweet with one simple word,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“Indeed.”</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Why Musk tweeted a cryptic message pertaining to virtual currency?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, it’s quite simple once you bring attention to how bitcoins are mined. Mining bitcoins requires a great amount of energy and time which means more energy is consumed since the process to mine just one bitcoin takes too long. On average, it takes 10 minutes and 72GW to mine one bitcoin. To run a bitcoin mining network, this means 113.89 GW per hour is used per year. Why do we care about the amount of energy being used to mine bitcoin? Well, the energy used is by burning fossil fuels and trading of bitcoin never ends on crypto exchanges. This means that they are being mined every hour, all around the year. As a law of direct proportionality, as the price of Bitcoin increases, so does the amount of energy consumed as miners mine coins with the price rise, attracting more users to join the Bitcoin network and the cycle goes on.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Two days later after Musk’s cryptic poll tweet, he <a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1392602041025843203/photo/1\">tweeted</a> that Tesla is not selling its bitcoins but it is stopping accepting bitcoin as a valid currency to purchase Tesla. Tesla supports cryptocurrency, but not at the cost of the environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is good news in the sense that now more efficient and energy-saving hardware will be made to mine bitcoins. This could lead to a more technologically advanced mining network as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'One Tweet Sends Bitcoin Crashing to an all-time Low In Three Months', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Economics,News &amp; Updates', '1623067744_andre-francois-mckenzie-vh7U_Z75L3U-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:09:04'),
(99, 'some-important-highlights-for-wednesday-stock-play', 'Tue, 25 May 2021 19:46:56 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>New Delhi:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As noted, Bulls held the post for the second consecutive day as the&nbsp;Nifty&nbsp;managed to close over the pivotal 15,100 level, enlisting the most noteworthy day by day close over the most recent 43 days. Purchasing interest in financials, auto and metals counters supported estimation as financial backers got more wealthy by Rs 2.8 lac crore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The index figured out how to frame a tiny bullish light on the every day chart, raising any expectations of additional potential gain. As per analysts, Nifty may observe further jump towards 15,200 and 15,350 levels in the event that it figures out how to hold the 15,100 level.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here\'s the way by which analysts assess the market trend:-&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mazhar Mohammad of Chartviewindia thinks Nifty requires to stay above the&nbsp;bullish void area&nbsp;present in the 15,043-14,938 zone. He said: “If this gap zone successfully offers support on dips, in course of time, the bulls can head higher to test their lifetime highs present around the 15,431 level. However, if the bulls fail to defend the 14,938 level on a closing basis, it can encourage the bears. Traders are advised to buy the weakness close to 15,000 level with a stop loss below 14,938 level on a closing basis.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was said by Gaurav Ratnaparkhi of Sharekhan that the list has crossed the 61.8 percent retracement of February-April fall and hopes to test the unsurpassed high of 15,431. Be that as it may, the assembly towards the high is probably not going to be an uneven excursion. There can be irregular interruption on the way up. The following obstacle is seen at 15,160 level, which is close the 78.6 percent retracement of February-April fall. The index can observe&nbsp; a short consolidation close to this key&nbsp;Fibonacci level&nbsp;before expanding higher. On the other side, any minor degree plunge is probably going to discover support close to the 15,000-14,940 zone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having that said, let us shed some light on some key indicators that are likely to be indicating the action for Monday</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The shares of US fall just when the telecom stocks drop down. S&amp;P 500 and the Dow also dropped on Tuesday, all this when sharp falls in telecom stocks. Alongside, a poor housing initiates data overshadowed upward earnings from Home Depot and the Waltmart. Moving forward around 9:10 pm IST, there was an average fall of Dow Jones at 83.75 points or in other words a percentage of 12 to 4158.30. The Nasdaq composite ended up gaining 49.22 points which makes in 0.37%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EU shares close to record highs</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>European stocks are seen closing record upward trends on Tuesday on optimism somewhat around several countries loosening up economic restrictions, dropping unemployment rate in the United Kingdom and powerful earnings report data from companies. At 9:10 p.m IST, the pan-European STOXX 600 index was at a rise of 0.26%, trading at a high record which it touched last week, with economy-related cyclical sectors such as oil, gas and miners, automakers heading with the gains. Last but not the least, the action of &nbsp; German DAX added on a 0.05% and Italy\'s FTSE MIB included 0.07%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Some Important Highlights for Wednesday Stock Play', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Hot Updates', '1623067712_nick-chong-N__BnvQ_w18-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:08:32'),
(100, 'us-banks-assuring-record-level-earning-in-2021', 'Tue, 01 Jun 2021 12:49:13 +0000', NULL, '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the years 2019 and 2020, the world economy faced a serious crisis to which every country became a victim; the Coronavirus pandemic erupted from China and affected every country across the globe. Every country that had to undergo major lockdowns really hit its economy hard on; where many were even expecting to get bankrupt because of the uncontrollable upheaval. This effect on the economy led to major spikes, and even faced a crashing stock market. The drop in the prices of the shares was due to the risk factor because the investors were deadly reluctant to invest a big amount occurring in the stocks in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>America faced a serious crisis in this aspect when all the investors started backing off and then as soon as the condition started getting better, the trading also started to settle down. At that time, the prime focus where all the investors got more interested was cryptocurrencies that made them hop back into the share market slowly and gradually. The second step was a big boost to the American banks that helped them gain the maximum amount of business, making them ready enough to emerge back in the business field.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Banks and investment:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to the market survey, it was observed that in the first quarter of the year 2021, the revenue was mainly generated through investment in the banking sector. It was observed that the generation of profit increased from 29.3% to 40.1%, which is a record-breaking for the business generated by the banks. The survey further elaborates that if the investment continues to increase with the same pace, then the total revenue generated will be enough to compensate for the loss that had affected the country in the times of the Covid pandemic. This time the markets are also increasing their share prices; which is a good sign for the investors to jump into the pool of investments, which can help the banks to boost their position in the global stock market in the coming future.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Institute of International Finance and their stance:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to IIF, the banks of America are now in such a position where they are self-sufficient to earn for the next year through the business generated by the banks. The maximum amount of profit has been generated by the Bank of America and JP Morgan Chase; these two banks have independently gained profits of about 29.3 percent and 40.4 percent, respectively. The analysts believe they are now independent enough to bring the maximum business to the country through the incorporation of their features and facilities, enabling the economy of the country to flourish and get back up from the point where it started sinking. This recovery has regained the trust of the investors in the banking sector, helping them to start investing more into these banks where they will be the source of business recovery and bringing the consumers to the country from all over the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'US banks assuring record level earning in 2021', NULL, 'Published', NULL, 'Business,Don\'t Miss,Hot Updates', '1623067677_vinayak-sharma-lyJerpl6cRM-unsplash.jpg', NULL, '2021-06-07 07:07:57');
